hadiths[467]{hadithnumber,text}:
2620,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney logon ko khutba irshad farmaya aur kaha : yaqinan Allah Taala ney tum par Haj farz kiya hai. eik aadmi kehney laga : har saal? aap khamosh rahey, yahan tak ke us ney teen dafa ye sawal dohraayaa. aap ney farmaya : agar main han, 'keh deta to har saal wajib ho jata aur agar har saal wajib ho jata to tum isey ada na kar saktey. jab tak main tumhein chhodey rahun, tum bhi mujhey chhodey raha karo. tum sey pehley key log apney anbiya sey ikhtilaf karney aur ziyada sawalaat karney ki wajeh hi sey halak huye. jab main tumhein kisi kaam ka hukm dun toi apni taqat key mutabiq uski pabandi karo aur jab tumhein kisi chiz sey rok dun to usey chhod do."
2621,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (khutbey key liye) khadey huye aur farmaya : Allah Taala ney tum par Haj farz farma diya hai. Hazrat Aqra bin Habis Tamimi (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool! kya har saal? aap khamosh ho gaey, phir farmaya : agar main han, keh deta to har saal wajib ho jata, phir na tum suntey aur na itaat kartey. Haj sirf eik hi (dafa farz) hai."
2622,Hazrat Amr bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat abu-Rizeen (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! merey walid bahut boodhey ho chukey hain. wo Haj o Umra balke safar tak ki taqat nahin rakhtey. aap ney farmaya : tum apney walid ki taraf sey Haj aur Umra karo.
2623,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Haj mabroor ka badla jannat key siwa kuch nahin. aur eik Umra dusrey Umerey tak key darmiyani gunahon ka kaffara ban jata hai."
2624,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Haj mabroor ka sawab sirf jannat hai. baqi riwayat taqriban sabiqa riwayat hi ki tarah hai. magar us riwayat mein farq sirf ye hai ke aap ney farmaya : eik Umra dusrey Umerey tak key darmiyani gunahon ko khatam kar deta hai."
2625,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : aey Allah key Rasool! kon sa amal sab sey afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala par emaan. us ney kaha : phir kon sa? aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad. us ney puchha : phir kon sa? aap ney farmaya : phir hajje-mabroor.
2626,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen shakhs Allah Taala key khususi mehman hain : jihad ko janey wala, Haj key liye safar karney wala aur Umerey ko janey wala."
2627,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : boodhey, bachey, kamzor aur aurat ka jihad Haj aur Umra karna hai."
2628,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney is ghar (baitullah) ka Haj kya aur us doran mein koi shahwani baat ki na fisq (kabeera gunah ka irtikab) kya, wo (gunahon sey) is tarah (pak saaf ho kar) palat'ta hai jaisey us din tha jab usey uski maa ney jana tha."
2629,ummul-Mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey guzarish ki : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya hum aurten bhi aap key sath jihad key liye na jaya keren? kyonkey main to Quran Majeed mein koi amal jihad sey afzal nahin paati. aap ney farmaya : nahin tum aurton key liye afzal aur khoobsurat tareen jihad baitullah ka Haj mabroor hai.
2630,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik Umra dusrey Umerey tak (key darmiyani gunahon) key liye kaffara ban jata hai, aur hajje-mabroor ki to jannat key siwa koi jaza hi nahin."
2631,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pay-dar-pay Haj aur Umra kartey raho kyonkey ye dono faqr aur gunahon ko is tarah zaayel kartey hain jaisey aag ki bhatti lohey key zang aur mail kuchail ko door karti hai.
2632,"Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Haj aur Umra musalsal kartey raho. yaqinan ye faqr aur gunahon ko is tarah zaayel kar detey hain jis tarah aag ki bhatti lohey soney aur chaandi key mail kuchail ko zaayel kar deti hai. aur Haj mabroor ka sawab to jannat sey kam nahin."
2633,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik aurat ney Haj ki nazar maana thi lekin wo (hajj kiye baghair) faut ho gaee. us ka bhai Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur us barey mein poochhney laga. aap ney farmaya : tera kya khayal hai ke agar teri behan key zimmey qarz hota to kya to usey ada karta? us ney arz kya : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : Allah ka qarz bhi ada karo kyonkey Allah Taala ziyada haq rakhta hai ke us ka qarz ada kya jaey.
2634,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aurat ney Hazrat sanaan bin Salma Johni (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey poochen ke uski ma ( farz ) Haj kiye baghair faut ho gaee hai. agar wo aurat apni maa ki taraf sey Haj kar ley to wo usey kifaayat kar jaeyga? aap ney farmaya : haan. agar uski maa key zimmey qarz hota aur wo aurat uski taraf sey ada kar deti to kya usey kifaayat na karta? usey chahiye ke wo apni maa ki taraf sey Haj kerey.
2635,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey apney walid key barey mein puchha jo (farz) Haj kiye baghair faut ho gaya tha. aap ney farmaya : to apney walid ki taraf sey Haj kar ley.
2636,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke « banu Khasam » ( qabiley ) ki eik aurat ney muzdalfa ki subh Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah Taala ki taraf sey logon par farz kiye gaey Haj ney merey walid ko is haal mein paya hai ke wo intehai boodhey hain, sawari par bhi nahin beth saktey, to kya main un ki taraf sey Haj kar sakti hun? aap ney farmaya : haan."
2637,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey (eik dusri sanad sey) sabiqa hadees ki misl riwayat aati hai.
2638,"Hazrat abu-Rizeen Uqeli (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey walid bahut boodhey ho chukey hain, Haj o Umra balke safar bhi nahin kar saktey. aap ney farmaya : tum apney walid ki taraf sey Haj aur Umra karo."
2639,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke « Khasam » qabiley ka eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur kehney laga : merey walid intehai boodhey hain. wo sawar nahin ho saktey. aur Allah key fariza Haj ney unhein aa liya hai. kya un ki taraf sey Haj karna in ko kifaayat kar jaeyga ? aap ney farmaya : kya to us ka sab sey bada beta hai? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : to bata agar terey walid key zimmey qarz hota to kya to usey ada karta ? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : phir to uski taraf sey Haj bhi kar.
2640,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey walid Haj kiye baghair faut ho gaey hain, to kya main un ki taraf sey Haj kar sakta hun? aap ney farmaya : batao agar tumharey walid par qarz hota to kya tum usey ada kartey? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : to Allah ka qarz adaegi ka ziyada haq daar hai."
2641,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha ke merey baap par Haj farz hai magar wo intehai boodhey hain. sawari par nahin beth saktey. aur agar main unhein (paalan par) baandh dun to khatra hai ke wo mar jaeyngey, to kya main unki taraf sey Haj kar sakta hun? farmaya : batao agar is par qarz hota aur tum ada kartey to kya usey kifaayat karta? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : phir tum apney baap ki taraf sey Haj bhi karo."
2642,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ( merey bhai ) Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechey oontni hi par sawar they ke khasam qabiley ki eik aurat aa kar aap sey masla poochhney lagi. Fazal usey dekhney lagey aur wo unhein dekhney lagi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Fazal ka chehra dusri taraf pher diya. wo aurat kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool! Allah Taala key fariza Haj ney, jo us ney apney bandon par aaid kya hai, merey walid ko bahut budhapey ki haalat mein paya hai. wo sawari par beth bhi nahin saktey. to kya main un ki taraf sey Haj kar sakti hun? aap ney farmaya : haan. (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ) ye Hajjatul-wadaa ki baat hai."
2643,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney khabar di ke Hajjatul-wadaa mein Khasam qabiley ki eik aurat ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey masla puchha, Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aap key peechey sawari par bethey they. wo kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool! Allah Taala key apney bandon par fariza Haj ney merey walid ko bahut budhapay ki haalat mein paya hai. wo sawari par beth bhi nahin saktey. agar main unki taraf sey Haj karun to kya un ki taraf sey kifaayat ho jaeyga? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan. Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) us aurat ko dekhney lagey (kyonkey) wo khush shakal thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Fazal ka chehra pakad kar dusri taraf pher diya."
2644,Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main (Hajjatul-wada mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sawari par aap key peechey betha tha ke eik aadmi aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool! meri walida bahut ziyada boodhi hain. agar main unhein utha kar sawari par bitha dun to wo beth nahin sakengi aur agar main unhein (paalan key sath) baandh dun to khatra hai ke wo mar jaeyngi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to bata agar teri walida key zimmey qarz hota to kya to ada karta? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : phir apni maa ki taraf sey to Haj bhi kar ley.
2645,"Hazrat ibn Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi sey farmaya : to apney walid ka sab sey bada beta hai, lihaza to uski taraf sey Haj kar."
2646,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney apna bacha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf haathon par buland kya aur kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya us ka bhi Haj hai? aap ney farmaya : han, aur sawab tujhey milega."
2647,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aurat ney apna bacha hodaj sey uthaya aur ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dikha kar aap sey) kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya us ka bhi Haj hoga? aap ney farmaya : haan. aur sawab tujhey milega.
2648,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik aurat ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf eik bacha uthaya aur kehney lagi : kya us ka bhi Haj hoga? aap ney farmaya : haan. aur sawab terey liye hai.
2649,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ( Haj sey) wapis (Madina Munawra ko) tashrif la rahey they. jab maqam Rauha par pahunchey to kuch logon sey miley. aap ney farmaya : tum kon ho? unhoney arz kya : hum musalman hain, phir wo kehney lagey : aap kon ho? haazirin ney bataya ke ye Allah key Rasool hain. to unki eik aurat ney doli sey eik bacha uthaya aur kehney lagi : kya iskey liye Haj hai? aap ney farmaya : haan. aur sawab terey liye hai."
2650,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey mazkur hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (hajj sey wapsi key doran mein) eik aurat key paas sey guzrey. wo pardey mein thi aur uskey sath uska eik bacha tha. wo kehney lagi : kya uskey liye Haj hai? aap ney farmaya : haan. aur sawab terey liye hai.
2651,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath (hajj key liye) chaley to zul-Qada key paanch din baqi they. hum (umuman) Haj hi ki niyat rakhtey they magar jab hum Makka Mukarrama key qarib huye to aap ney hukm farmaya : jinkey sath qurbani ka janwer nahin, wo jab baitullah ka tawaf kar chuken to ehraam khatam kar den (halal ho jaeyn)."
2652,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Madiney waley Zul-Hulefa sey, Sham waley Johfa sey aur Najad waley Qarnul-manazil sey ehraam bandhein. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : aur Yamen waley « yalamlam » sey ehraam bandhein."
2653,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik aadmi masjid mein khada huwa aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool! aap hamen kahan sey ehraam baandhney ka hukm detey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Madina Munawra waley Zul-Hulefa sey, Sham waley Johfa sey aur Najad waley Qarnul-Manazil sey ehram bandhein. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke log kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye bhi farmaya tha : Yamen waley yalamlam sey Ehram bandhein. main ye jumla Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey nahin samajh saka (yani barahe-rast aap sey akhaz nahin kya balke dusrey sahaba sey akhaz kya hai.)"
2654,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Madina Munawra walon key liye Zul-Hulefa, Sham aur Misr walon key liye Johfa Iraq walon key liye zaat arq aur Yamen walon key liye Yalamlam meeqat muqarrar farmaey."
2655,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Madina Munawra walon key liye Zul-Hulefa, Sham walon key liye Johfa, Najad walon key liye Qarnul-Manazil aur Yamen walon key liye yalamlam meeqaat muqarrar farmaey, neez farmaya : ye meeqaat un ilaqon (key logon) key liye hain aur unkey liye bhi jo un Mawaqit sey guzrein, chahey wo dusrey ilaqon sey talluq rakhtey hain. aur jis shakhs ki rihaaish un Mawaqit key andar ho to wo jahan sey ( Umerey aur Haj ka) safar shuru keren, wahin sey ehraam baandhen yahan tak ke ye hukm makkey walon par bhi laagu hoga, yani ehal Makka, Makka Mukarrama hi sey ehraam bandhengey."
2656,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Madiney waley Zul-Hulefa sey, Sham waley Johfa sey aur Najad waley Qarn ( Manazil ) sey ehram bandhein. aur mujhey bataya gaya hai, mainey khud nahin suna ke aap ney farmaya tha : Yamen waley yalamlam sey ehraam bandhein."
2657,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Madina Munawra walon key liye Zul-Hulefa, Sham aur Misr walon key liye Johfa, iraaq walon key liye Zaat arq, Najad walon key liye Qarn aur Yamen walon key liye yalamlam ko meeqat muqarrar farmaya hai."
2658,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Madina Munawra walon key liye Zul-Hulefa, Sham walon key liye Johfa, Najad walon key liye Qarn aur Yamen walon key liye yalamlam ko miqaat muqarrar farmaya. aap ney farmaya : ye Mawaqit un (ilaqon key logon ) key liye hain. aur un logon key liye bhi jo dusrey ilaqon sey hon lekin un Mawaqit sey guzrein b-sharte-ke wo Haj o Umra key iraday sey ayen. aur jo log un Mawaqit key andar rehtey hon to wo un jagahon sey ehram baandhen jahan sey chalen, yahan tak ke ye hukm makkey walon par bhi laagu hoga (ke wo makkey hi sey Haj ka ehraam baandhen)."
2659,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Madina Munawra walon key liye Zul-Hulefa, Sham walon key liye Johfa, Yamen walon key liye Yalamlam aur Najad walon key liye Qarn (Manazil ) ko meeqaat muqarrar farmaya. ye Mawaqit un logon key liye hain aur unkey liye jo dusrey ilaqon sey aa kar yahan sey guzrein, b-sharte-ke wo Haj ya Umerey ka irada rakhtey hon. aur jo log un Mawaqit key andar rehtey hon, wo apney ghar hi sey ehraam baandhen yahan tak ke Makka Mukarrama waley Makka Mukarrama hi sey ehraam bandhen."
2660,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ibtidaa Zul-Hulefa mein raat guzari aur uski masjid mein namaz padhi.
2661,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Zul-Hulefa mein apney padaaw ki jagah mein they ke aap ko khuwab aaya. aap sey kaha gaya : aap eik ba-barkat wadi mein hain.
2662,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Zul-Hulefa ki wadi muqaddas mein padaaw dala aur wahan namaz padhi.
2663,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Zohar ki namaz beda mein padhi, phir sawar huye aur beda key pahad par chadhey. aur namaz Zohar key baad Haj o Umerey ka ehraam baandha."
2664,Hazrat Asma bint Umes (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke maqam Beda mein unhoney Muhammad bin abu-Bakar Siddiq ko jana. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney is baat ka tazkira Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kya to aap ney farmaya : Asma sey kaho wo ghusl karey aur ehraam baandh ley.
2665,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Hajjatul-wadaa key moqey par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Haj key liye nikley. unkey sath un ki biwi Asma binte Umes (Raziallahu anha) bhi thin jin ka talluq Khasam qabiley sey tha. jab wo Zul-Hulefa mein they to Asma ney Muhammad bin Abu-Bakar ko janm diya. (ye dekh kar) Abu-Bakar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur soorate-haal sey muttala kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya ke Asma sey kaho, wo ghusl kerey. phir Haj ka ehraam baandh ley aur jo kuchh log keren, wo bhi karti rahey magar baitullah ka tawaf na kerey."
2666,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Hunain sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) ka Abwa key maqam par ikhtilaf ho gaya. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mohrim apna sar dho sakta hai. aur Hazrat Miswar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : wo sar nahin dho sakta. mujhey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bheja ke un sey is barey mein poochhun. (main aaya) to mainey unhein kunwen ki do lakdiyon key darmiyan ghusl kartey paya. unhoney eik kapdey key sath parda kiya huwa tha. mainey unhein salam kiya aur kaha : mujhey Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap key paas bheja hai ke aap sey poochhun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ehraam ki haalat mein apna sar kaisey dhotey they? Hazrat Abu-Ayyub ney kapdey par haath rakh kar usey nichey kiya yahan tak ke unka sar nazar aaney laga, phir us shakhs sey kehney lagey : jo unkey sar par pani baha raha tha : pani bahao, phir unhoney apney sar ko apney dono haathon sey harkat di, apney dono haathon ko aagey laye aur peechhey ley gaey. aur farmaya : mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey kartey dekha hai."
2667,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke mohrim za'fraan ya waras sey rangey huye kapdey pehney.
2668,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha gaya : mohrim kon sey kapdey pehan sakta hai? aap ney farmaya : wo qamis, Brandi (topi daar kurta), shalwaar, pagdi, aisa kapda jisey waras ya za'fraan laga ho aur mozey nahin pehan sakta magar ye ke uskey paas jootey na hon to wo mozey pehan ley magar unhein takhnon sey nichey kaat (kar jooton ki tarah bana) ley."
2669,"Hazrat Yaala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mainey kaha : kaash! ! main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko nuzooley-wahi ki haalat mein dekhun. eik baar hum (dorane-safar mein) Jaarana key maqam par they jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney khemey mein they ke aap par ""wahi"" utarney lagi. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujhey ishara farmaya ke aa jao. mainey apna sar khemey mein dakhil kiya. darasal eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya tha jisney jubbey mein Umerey ka ehraam baandh liya tha. us aadmi ney khushbu bhi lagai hui thi. us ney aap sey puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap us shakhs key barey mein kya farmatey hain jisney jubbey hi mein ehraam baandh liya ho? to aap par ""wahi"" utarney lagi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uski wajeh sey kharratey leney lagey. kuchh der baad aap sey ye haalat door hui to aap ney farmaya : kahan hai wo shakhs jisney abhi mujh sey sawal kiya tha? us aadmi ko laya gaya. aap ney farmaya : jubba utaar dey aur khushbu dho dal, phir naey sirey sey ehraam baandh. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke ( ثُمَّ أَحْدِثْ اِحْرَامًا ) phir naey sirey sey ehraam baandh. key alfaz merey ilm key mutabiq Nuh bin Habib key ilawa kisi raawi ney bayan nahin kiye, is liye main in alfaz ko mehfooz nahin samajhta. (Allah ki qism Allah hi behtar jaanta hai.)"
2670,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : mohrim kon sey kapdey pehan sakta hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qamis, pagdi, pajama ( shalwaar ) topi-daar kurta (Brandi) aur mozey na pehney, haan agar uskey paas jootey na hon to chamdey key mozey pehan sakta hai magar unhein takhnon key nichey sey kaat ley. aur aisey kapdey na pehno jinhein za'fraan ya waras lagi hui ho."
2671,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! jab hum ehraam baandhen to hum kon sey kapdey pahnen? aap ney farmaya : qamis, pagdi, shalwaar aur mozey na pahno magar ye ke kisi key paas jootey na hon to wo mozon ko takhnon sey nichey kaat ley. aur aisey kapdey na pahno jin ko waras ya za'fraan lagi hui ho."
2672,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko khutba detey suna, aap farma rahey they : jis shakhs key paas tehband na ho, wo shalwaar pehan sakta hai aur jis key paas jootey na hon, wo mozey pehan sakta hai."
2673,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huye suna : jis shakhs (mohrim) key paas tehband na ho, wo shalwaar pehan sakta hai aur jis shakhs key paas jootey na hon, wo mozey pehan sakta hai."
2674,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi khada ho kar kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! ehraam ki haalat mein aap hamein kin kapdon key pehanney ka hukm detey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qamis, shalwaar, pagdi, Brandi (aur kot aur topi-daar kurta) aur mozey na pahno magar ye ke kisi key paas jootey na hon to wo mozey takhnon key nichey sey kaat kar pehan sakta hai. aur koi aisa kapda na pahno jis ko za'fraan ya waras lagi ho, isi ke sath mohrim aurat na naqab baandhey aur na dastaney pehney."
2675,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : mohrim kon sey kapdey pehan sakta hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qamis, pagdi, shalwaar (pajama waghera), topi-daar kurta aur mozey na pahno, haan agar kisi key paas jootey na hon to wo mozon ko takhnon sey nichey kaat kar pehan ley. aur koi aisa kapda na pahno jisey za'fraan ya waras lagi ho."
2676,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha ke jab hum ehraam baandhen to kon sey kapdey pahnen? aap ney farmaya : qamis, shalwaar, pagdi, Brandi (topi-daar kurta) aur mozey na pahno magar ye ke kisi key paas jootey na hon to takhnon sey nichey mozey pehan ley (yani ooper sey kaat dey). aur koi aisa kapda na pahno jisey waras ya za'fraan lagi ho."
2677,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik aadmi ney buland aawaz sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pukara aur kaha : jab hum ehraam baandhen to kon sey kapdey pahnen? aap ney farmaya : qamis, pagdi, shalwaar, Brandi aur mozey na pehan, haan agar tumhein jootey na milen to mozon ko takhnon sey nichey nichey pehan lo. (yani ooper sey kaat do.)"
2678,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko buland aawaz sey pukara aur kaha : jab hum ehraam baandhen to kya pahnen? aap ney farmaya : qamis, pagdi, brandi (topi-daar karta), shalwaar (pajama waghera) aur mozey na pahno siwaye iske ke jootey na hon. aisi surat mein takhnon sey nichey mozey pehney ja saktey hain. aur koi aisa kapda bhi na pahno jo waras ya za'fraan sey ranga huwa ho."
2679,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : tum ehraam ki haalat mein qamis, shalwaar, pagdi, brandi aur mozey na pahno."
2680,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : jab koi shakhs (mohrim) tehband na paey to shalwaar pehan sakta hai aur jab jootey na paey to mozey pehan sakta hai lekin wo inhein takhnon key nichey sey kaat ley.
2681,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab mohrim key paas jootey na hon to wo mozey pehan ley magar unhein takhnon key nichey sey kaat ley.
2682,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke eik aadmi khada ho kar kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap hamein ehraam ki haalat mein kis qisam key kapdey pehanney ka hukm detey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum qamis, shalwaar aur mozey na pahno magar kisi aadmi key paas jootey na hon to wo takhnon sey nichey mozey pehan ley (aur takhnon sey ooper wala hissa kaat dey). aur koi aisa kapda na pehney jisey za'fraan ya waras lagi ho. mohrim aurat naqab na baandhey aur dastaney bhi na pehney."
2683,"Ummul-Mominin Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey arz ki : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya wajeh hai ke log ehraam sey halal ho gaey hain magar aap Umra kar key halal nahin huye? aap ney farmaya : mainey apney sar key baalon ko gond sey chipkaaya hai aur qurbani key janwer ko qalaada (haar) pehnaa diya hai, is liye main halal nahin ho sakta yahan tak ke Haj sey halal ho jaun."
2684,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko talbeed ki haalat mein labbaik pukartey dekha.
2685,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko apney haathon sey khushbu lagai aap key ehraam key waqt jab aap ney ehraam ka irada farmaya aur halal honey (ehraam kholney) key waqt (khushbu lagai) pehley is sey ke aap mukammal halal hon.
2686,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko khushbu lagai aap key ehraam key waqt ehraam baandhney sey pehley aur aap key halal honey (ehraam kholney) key waqt tawafe ziyaarat karney sey pehley.
2687,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aap key ehraam key waqt ehraam baandhney sey pehley aur halal honey key waqt khushbu lagai.
2688,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aap key ehraam key waqt khushbu lagai jab aap ney ehraam baandha. aur jab aap Jamraa-Aqba ko rami karney key baad halal huye us waqt bhi khushbu lagai is sey pehley ke aap baitullah ka tawaf farmaeyn.
2689,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko halal hotey waqt khushbu lagai aur ehraam baandhney key waqt bhi aisi khushbu lagai jo tumhari is khushbu ki tarah nahin thi, yani jo baqi nahin rehti."
2690,"Hazrat Urwa bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha : aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko kon si khushbu lagai thi? unhoney farmaya : mainey aap ko sab sey behtareen khushbu lagai, ehraam baandhney key waqt bhi aur halal honey key waqt bhi."
2691,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aap key ehraam baandhney key waqt behtareen khushbu lagaya karti thi jo merey paas hoti thi.
2692,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aap key ehraam baandhney key waqt aur halal honey key waqt aur jab aap baitullah ka tawafey-ziyaarat karney chaley, apney paas mojud behtareen khushbu lagai."
2693,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aap key ehraam baandhney sey qabl aur qurbani waley din tawafey-baitullah karney sey pehley khushbu lagai jis mein kastoori shamil thi.
2694,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mujhey yun mehsus ho raha hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sar mubarak mein khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun jabkey aap haalatey-ehraam mein hun. (ustaad) Ahmed bin Nasar ki hadees mein hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki mang mein (dorane-ehraam) kastoori ki khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun.
2695,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke doraney ehraam Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki mang mubarak mein khushbu ki chamak saaf nazar aati thi.
2696,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mujhey yun lagta hai ke main jabkey aap ehraam ki haalat mein hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sar mubarak mein khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun."
2697,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key baalon ki jadon mein khushbu ki chamak dekha karti thi jabkey aap ehram ki halat mein hotey they.
2698,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke mujhey aisey mehsus hota hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sar mubarak ki mang mein khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun jabkey aap ehraam ki haalat mein hain.
2699,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : tehqiq mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sar mubarak mein khushbu ki chamak dekhi jabkey aap ehraam ki haalat mein they.
2700,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : goya ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki mang mubarak mein khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun jabkey aap labbaik pukar rahey they.
2701,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam), Hannad (raawi) ney (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key bajaey) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam), jab ehraam baandhney ka irada farmatey to apney paas mojud behtareen khushbu lagatey yahan tak ke main uski chamak aap key sar aur dadhi mubarak mein dekha karti thi."
2702,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ehraam sey qabl apney paas mojud behtareen khushbu lagati thi yahan tak ke main us khushbu ki chamak aap key sar aur dadhi mubarak mein dekhti thi.
2703,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke tehqiq mainey (ehram baandhney sey) teen din baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki mang mubarak mein khushbu ki chamak dekhi.
2704,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main ( ehraam baandhney sey) teen din baad bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki mang mubarak mein khushbu ki chamak dekha karti thi.
2705,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Muntashir sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey ehraam baandhtey waqt khushbu laganey key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : is sey to achcha ye hai ke main gandhak mal lun. mainey ye baat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey zikr ki to wo farmaney lagin : Allah Taala abu Abdur-Rehman ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ) par reham farmaai ! main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko khushbu lagaya karti thi, phir aap apni biwiyon key paas jatey, phir subh hoti jabkey aap sey khushbu ki mehak aa rahi hoti thi (aur aap subh ko ehraam baandhtey)."
2706,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Muntashir bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna ke main gandhak mal lun to ziyada achcha hai bajaey iskey ke mujh sey ehraam ki haalat mein khushbu ki mehak aaye. main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaya aur unhein ye baat batai to unhoney farmaya : mainey khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko khushbu lagai. aap apni biwiyon key paas gaey, phir aap ney ehraam baandha (aur aap sey mehak aati thi)."
2707,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mard ko Zafran laganey sey mana farmaya.
2708,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (mard ko) Zafran laganey sey mana farmaya hai.
2709,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Zafran laganey sey mana farmaya hai. Hammad raawi kehtey hain : yani mardon ko.
2710,"Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya. us ney Umerey ka ehraam baandh rakha tha lekin us ney siley huye kapdey pehney huye they aur Khalooq (khushbu) laga rakhi thi. usney aap sey kaha : mainey Umerey ka ehraam baandha hai to main kya karun? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to Haj mein kya karta tha? us ney kaha : main is (siley huye kapdey) sey bachta tha aur is ( khushbu ) ko dho diya karta tha. aap ney farmaya : jo to Haj mein karta tha, wohi Umerey mein kar."
2711,"Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik aadmi aaya jabkey aap Jaarana mein tashrif farma they. us aadmi ney jubba pehna huwa tha aur apni dadhi aur sar ko zard rang ki khushbu laga rakhi thi. wo kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool! mainey Umerey ka ehraam baandha hai aur meri haalat aap dekh rahey hain. aap ney farmaya : jubba utar dey aur rang daar khushbu dho dey aur jis tarah to Haj (key ehraam) main karta tha, isi tarah Umerey (key ehram) main kar."
2712,Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Mohrim key barey mein farmaya : jab usey sar ya aakhon mein takleef ho to apni aakhon par eilwey ka lep kerey.
2713,"Hazrat Muhammad ( Baaqar ) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke hum Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) key paas hazir huye aur hamney un sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Haj ( Hajjatul-wadaa ) key barey mein puchha to unhoney hum sey bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : agar mujhey is baat ka pehley pata chal jata jis ka baad mein pata chala hai to main qurbani key janwer sath na lata aur Haj key bajaey Umerey ka ehraam baandhta, lihaza jis shakhs key sath qurbani ka janwer nahin, wo Haj key ehraam ko Umerey key ehraam mein badal ley. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Yamen sey qurbani key janwer ley kar aaye they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Madina Munawra sey qurbani key janwer laye they. Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney rang daar kapdey pehney huye they aur surma laga rakha tha. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main bhadkaane (ghussa dilaney) key liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas masla poochhney gaya. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! Fatima ney rang daar kapdey pehney huye hain aur surma laga rakha hai aur wo kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey un kamon ka hukm diya hai? aap ney farmaya is ney sach kaha. wo sach kehti hai, wo sachi hai, main hi ney usey hukm diya hai."
2714,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi (ehraam ki haalat mein) apni sawari sey gir pada. us (sawari) ney usey fauran maar dala. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey pani aur beri key patton sey ghusl do aur usey ( ehraam waley ) do kapdon mein kafan diya jaey. sar aur chehra nanga rahey kyonkey ye qiyamat key din labbaik kehta huwa uthega.
2715,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik (Mohrim) aadmi faut ho gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey pani aur beri key patton sey ghusl do aur uskey (ehraam key) kapdon hi mein usey kafna do. aur uskey chehrey aur sar ko na dhaanpo. ye qiyamat key din labbaik kehta huwa uthega.
2716,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sirf Haj ka ehraam baandha tha.
2717,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sirf Haj ki labbaik kahi.
2718,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath zul-hijja ka chaand tulu honey sey chand din qabl ( Haj ko) nikley. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey jo shakhs sirf Haj ka ehraam baandhna chahey, wo Haj ka ehraam baandhey aur jo Umerey ka ehraam baandhna chahey, wo Umerey ka ehraam baandhey."
2719,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath nikley to hamara irada yehi tha ke ye sirf Haj hai.
2720,"Hazrat Sabi bin Maabad bayan kartey hain ke main Erabi (dehati) aur Esai tha, phir main musalman ho gaya. mujhey jihad ka bahut shoq tha lekin mujhey pata chala ke mujh par to Haj aur Umra farz hain. main apney qabiley key eik aadmi key paas aaya jinka naam Harim bin Abdullah tha. mainey un sey us barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : dono b-yak waqt kar lo, phir qurbani ka jo janwer muyassar ho zibeh kar dena. mainey dono ka ehraam baandh liya. jab hum Azeeb maqam par pahunchey to mujhey Salman bin Rabeea aur Hazrat Zaid bin Sohaan miley. main Haj aur Umerey ki labbaik keh raha tha to un mein sey eik ney dusrey sey kaha ke ye shakhs to apney oont sey ziyada samajh daar malum nahin hota. main Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas hazir huwa aur arz ki : aey ameerul-momeneen ! mainey Islam qubul kya hai. mujhey jihad ka bahut shoq hai lekin mainey Haj aur Umra apney aap par farz paya hai. mein hareem bin Abdullah key paas gaya. mainey kaha : aey wo (Hurem) ! mainey apney aap par Haj aur Umra dono ko farz paya hai (to main kya karun?) unhoney kaha : dono ka ehraam ikhatta baandh lo, phir jo qurbani muyassar ho, zibeh kar dena. mainey dono ka ehraam baandh liya. jab main Uzeb maqam par pahuncha to mujhey Hazrat Salman bin Rabeea aur Zaid bin Sohaan miley to un mein sey eik ney dusrey sey kaha : ye apney oont sey ziyada samajhdar nahin. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : tumhein tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat ki tofiq mili hai."
2721,"Hazrat Sabi ney (mazkura baala ) key misl hadees bayan ki. kaha : phir main Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa, phir pura qissa (waqiaa) bayan kya lekin « یَا ھَنَّاہُ !  aey wo hareem ! key alfaz bayan nahin kiye."
2722,"Hazrat Shaqeeq bin Salma abu-Waeil sey riwayat hai ke bano taghlab key eik shakhs jinhein Sabi bin Maabad kaha jata tha aur wo pehley Esai they, phir wo musalman ho gaey, apney pehley Haj ko aaye to unhoney Haj aur Umerey ki b-yak waqt labbaik kahi. wo isi tarah dono ki b-yak waqt labbaik kehtey ja rahey they ke unka guzar Salman bin Rabeea aur Zaid bin Sohaan key qarib sey huwa to un mein sey eik ney kaha : to to apney us oont sey bhi kam aql hai. Hazrat Sabi ney kaha : mujhey us baat sey bahut pareshani hui yahan tak ke main Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey mila to mainey ye sari baat unkey gosh guzar ki. wo farmaney lagey : tumhein tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat mutahra ki tofiq mili hai. Hazrat Shaqeeq ney kaha : main aur Hazrat Masruq bin Ajdaa Hazrat Sabi bin Maabad key paas b-kasrat aatey jatey they aur un sey ye waqia sunaney ki guzarish kartey they."
2723,Hazrat Marwan bin Hakam sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat Usman key paas betha huwa tha ke unhoney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko Haj aur Umerey ki ikhatti labbaik kehtey suna : Hazrat Usman farmaney lagey : kya aap ko ilm nahin ke is sey roka gaya hai? Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey : yaqinan ilm hai magar mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dono ki ikhatti labbaik kehtey suna hai. main tumharey hukm ki wajeh sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka farman nahin chhod sakta.
2724,Hazrat Marwan sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney tamatto aur Quran sey roka to Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney elania Haj aur Umerey ki ikhatti labbaik padhi. Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aap aisa kartey hain jabkey mainey us sey rok rakha hai? Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : logon mein sey kisi shakhs key kehney sey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat nahin chhod sakta.
2725,nazar ney Shoba sey isi sanad sey is jaisi riwayat bayan ki hai.
2726,"Hazrat Baraa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yamen ka ameer banaya to main bhi unkey sath tha. jab wo ( Hajjatul-wadaa key moqey par Yamen sey) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye to Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tu ney ehraam kaisey baandha hai? mainey arz kya : mainey to aap key ehraam ki tarah ehraam baandha hai. aap ney farmaya : main to qurbani key janwer bhi sath laya hun aur mainey Haj o Umerey ka ikhatta ehraam baandha hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney sahaba sey farmaya tha : agar mujhey us hukm ka pehley pata chal jata jiska baad mein pata chala (yani Umerey key wajib honey ka) to main isi tarah karta jaisey tumney kya, lekin main to qurbani key janwer sath laya hun, lihaza mera Haj o Umra ikhatta hoga."
2727,"Hazrat Imran bin Husein (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Haj aur Umra ikhatta kya, phir aap faut ho gaey, na to aap ney (us sey) roka aur na Quran mein uski hurmat ka hukm nazil huwa."
2728,"Hazrat Imran (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Haj o Umra ikhatta kya, phir (us sey rokney key barey mein) koi hukm nazil nahin huwa, na Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey mana farmaya. (baad mein) eik shakhs (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ) ney apni raey sey uskey barey mein jo chaha kya."
2729,Hazrat Imran bin Husein (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tamatto kya. Imam abu Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke Ismaaeel bin Muslim naam key teen raawiye-hadees hain. un mein sey eik to yehi hain. un par koi aetraz nahin. dusrey buzurg wo hain jo Abu-Tufel sey bayan kartey hain. un mein bhi koi kharabi nahin. teesrey Ismaaeel bin Muslim Hazrat Zohri aur Hazrat Hasan sey bayan kartey hain. wo muhaddeseen key nazdik matrukul-hadees (ghair moatabar) hain.
2730,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ( لَبَّیْکَ عُمْرَۃً وَّ حَجًّا ) aey Allah! main terey samney Haj o Umerey key liye hazir hun. farmatey huye suna.
2731,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Haj aur Umra dono ki b-yak waqt labbaik kehtey suna.
2732,Hazrat Bakr bin Abdullah Muzni (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney bayan kya ke mainey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Umra o Haj ki ikhatti labbaik farmatey suna. mainey ye baat Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan ki to wo kehney lagey : aap ney sirf Haj ki labbaik kahi thi. main phir Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko mila aur un sey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat bayan ki. aap farmaney lagey : tum hamen bachey hi samajhtey ho. mainey khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ( لَبَّیْکَ عُمْرَۃً وَّ حَجًّا مَعًا ) farmatey suna hai.
2733,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hajjatul-wadaa mein Haj sey pehley Umerey ka faeyda uthaya tha aur qurbani bhi ki thi. aap Zul-Hulefa hi sey apney sath qurbani key janwer ley kar chaley they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pehley Umerey ki labbaik pukaari phir Haj ki labbaik pukaari aur logon ney bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Haj sey pehley Umra karney ka faeyda uthaya. kuch log qurbani key janwer sath laye they, kuch nahin laye they. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil honey key qarib they, aap ney logon sey farmaya : tum mein sey jo shakhs qurbani laya hai, is par koi haram chiz halal nahin hogi (uska ehraam khatam nahin hoga ) yahan tak ke wo apna Haj pura kerey. aur jo shakhs qurbani ka janwer nahin laya, wo baitullah ka tawaf kerey. Safa Marwa ki saee karey aur baal katwa kar halal ho jaey, phir (hajj key dino mein) Haj ka ehraam baandhey. aur phir qurbani bhi zibeh kerey. aur agar wo qurbani ki taqat na rakhta ho to wo doran Haj teen rozey rakhey aur jab apney ghar wapis jaey to saat rozey rakhey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Makka Mukarrama tashrif laye to aap ney tawaf farmaya. sab sey pehley Hajar Aswad ko bosa diya, phir tawaf key saat chakkaron mein sey pehley teen chakkar qadrey dorr kar purey kiye aur baqi chaar chakkar aaram sey chaley, phir jab baitullah ka tawaf pura farma liya to maqam Ibrahim key paas do rakat namaz padhi, phir salam pher kar mudey aur Safa par aaye aur Safa Marwa key bhi saat chakkar lagaey, phir aap kisi haram chiz sey halal na huye yahan tak ke aap ney apna Haj pura farmaya aur nahar ( das zil-Hijja) waley din apney qurbani key janwer zibeh farmaai aur wapis aa kar baitullah ka tawaf farmaya, phir aap par har wo chiz halal ho gaee jo (ehraam ki wajeh sey) haram hui thi. jo log qurbani key janwer sath laye they, unhoney bhi aisey hi kya jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kya tha."
2734,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Ali aur Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) dono Haj ko gaey. abhi raastey hi mein they ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney (bahaisiyat khalifa) tamattoa sey mana farma diya. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey : jab tum Hazrat Usman ko kooch kartey dekho to tum bhi sath hi kooch karna. Hazrat Ali aur unkey dusrey sathiyon ney (kooch key waqt) Umerey ki labbaik (buland aawaz sey) kahi to Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhein na roka. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney (Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey) kaha : mujhey to bataya gaya tha ke aap tamatto sey roktey hain? Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : zarur. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : kya aap ko ilm nahin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tamatto farmaya. unhoney kaha : kyon nahin?
2735,Hazrat Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Haris bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Suhak bin Qais ko Haj sey pehley Umerey ka faeyda uthaney ka tazkira kartey suna. ye us saal ki baat hai jis saal Hazrat Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) Haj key liye tashrif laye they. Suhak kehney lagey : ye kaam (tamatto) to wohi kar sakta hai jo Allah Taala key ehkam sey na-waqif ho. Hazrat Saad farmaney lagey : aey bhateejey! tu ney buri baat kahi hai. Suhak ney kaha : Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney to us sey roka tha. Saad (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey : ye Allah key Rasool ney kya hai aur hamney bhi aap key sath kya tha.
2736,Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) tamatto key jawaz ka fatwa diya kartey they. eik aadmi ney un sey kaha : is qism ka fatwa deney sey ruk jao. shayad aap ko pata nahin ke tumharey baad ameerul-momeneen (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ) ney uskey barey mein kya naya hukm jari farmaya hai. (Hazrat Abu-Musa ney kaha : ) main Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey mila to mainey un sey puchha. wo farmaney lagey : tehqiq! mujhey bhi malum hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye kya hai magar mainey achcha na samjha ke log raat ko peelu key darakhton key nichey biwiyon key sath jima kartey rahen aur phir Haj ko jaeyn to unkey saron sey ( ghusle-janabat key) pani key qatrey gir rahey hon.
2737,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna ke Allah ki qism ! main tumhein tamatto sey rokta hun, halanke main janta hun ke uska zikr Allah ki kitab mein hai aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye kya hai, yani Haj sey pehley Umra karna."
2738,"Hazrat Taoos sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya aap ko pata hai ke mainey Marwa key paas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sar key baal kaatey they? ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : nahin. ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke ye Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko tamatto sey roktey hain, halanke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tamatto kya tha."
2739,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main ( Yamen sey) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ( Hajjatul-wadaa key moqey par) Bat-ha mein hazir huwa to aap ney farmaya : tuney kya ehraam baandha hai? mainey kaha : mainey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ehraam ki tarah ehraam baandha hai. aap ney farmaya : qurbani ka koi janwer sath laya hai? mainey kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir baitullah ka tawaf kar aur Safa Marwa ki saee kar aur halal ho ja. mainey baitullah ka tawaf kya. Safa Marwa ki saee ki, phir main apni qom ki eik aurat key paas aaya. usney merey sar mein kanghi ki aur mera sar dhoya. main Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key daur mein yehi fatwa diya karta tha (ke Haj tamatto jayez hai ). eik dafa mein mausam Haj mein khada (ye fatwaa dey raha) tha ke merey paas eik aadmi aaya aur kehney laga : shayad aap ko malum nahin ke ameerul-momeneen (Hazrat Umar) (Raziallahu anhu) ney Haj key barey main eik naya hukm jari kar diya hai (ke tamatto na kya jaey ). mainey kaha : aey logo ! jisey hamney (is qism ka) koi fatwaa diya hai, wo zara thehar jaey (us par amal na kerey) Hazrat ameerul-momeneen tumharey paas aaney hi waley hain to unki iqtida (pairvi) karna. jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye to mainey arz kya : ameerul-momeneen! kya ( ajeeb ) hukm hai jo aap ney Haj key barey mein jari kya hai? wo farmaney lagey : agar hum Allah ki kitab ko lein to Allah Taala ney farmaya hai : Haj aur Umra Allah Taala key liye pura karo. (yani darmiyan halal na ho) aur agar hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat ko lein to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) halal nahin huye they yahan tak ke aap ney qurbani zibeh farmaey."
2740,"Hazrat Mutrif farmatey hain ke Hazrat Imran bin Husein (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujh sey kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tamatto farmaya. hamney bhi aap key sath tamatto kya, phir eik kehney waley ney apni raey sey kaha (ke tamatto nahin karna chahiye )."
2741,"Hazrat Muhammad ( Baaqar ) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke hum Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye aur un sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Haj key barey mein puchha to unhoney bayan farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Madiney mein rehtey huye no saal ho chukey they, phir ( daswen saal ) tamam logon mein aelan kar diya gaya ke us saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Haj key liye tashrif ley jaeyngey, lihaza bahut ziyada log Madina Munawra aa gaey. har eik ki khahish thi ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Haj karey aur jis tarah aap Haj keren, wo bhi isi tarah kerey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Haj key liye nikley to zul-Qada key paanch din baqi they. hum bhi aap key sath nikley. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey darmiyan they. aap par wahi utarti thi aur aap hi Quran Majeed ki sahih tafseer jantey they, lihaza jo aap ney kya, hamney bhi kya. hum (Madina Munawra sey) nikley to hamari niyat Haj hi ki thi."
2742,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hum (Hajjatul-wadaa mein) nikley to hamari niyat sirf Haj ki thi. jab hum sarf key maqam par pahunchey to mujhey haiz shuru ho gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye to main ro rahi thi. aap ney farmaya : kya tujhey haiz shuru ho gaya hai? mainey kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : (koi baat nahin) ye aisi chiz hai jo Adam ki betiyon par Allah Taala ki taraf sey muqarrar hai, lihaza jo dusrey ehram waley keren, to bhi karti reh magar baitullah ka tawaf na karna."
2743,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke main (Hajjatul-wadaa key moqey par) Yamen sey aaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Batha (Makka) main padaaw dal rakha tha. aap ney farmaya : tu ney ehraam baandha hai? mainey arz kya : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : kaisey baandha hai? unhoney kaha : mainey kaha tha is ehraam key sath jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka ehraam hai, labbaik kehta hun. aap ney farmaya : baitullah ka tawaf karo aur Safa Marwa ki saee karo aur halal ho jao. mainey isi tarah kya, phir main (apney qabiley ki) eik aurat key paas aaya to usney merey sar sey juein nikalin. main logon ko usi baat ka fatwa diya karta tha (ke tamatto jayez hai) yahan tak ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilaafat ka daur aa gaya to eik aadmi ney mujh sey kaha : aey Abu-Musa! apna ye fatwa rok lo. shayad tum nahin jantey ke ameerul-momeneen ney tumharey baad Haj key barey mein kya naya hukm jari kya hai? mainey kaha : aey logo ! jis shakhs ko hamney ye fatwa diya ho, wo zara intizar kar ley (yani is par amal na kerey), Hazrat ameerul-momeneen tumharey paas tashrif laney waley hain to tum unkey hukm ki pabandi karna. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) (aaye to merey istifsaar par) kehney lagey : agar hum Allah ki kitab ko lein to wo hamen mukammal karney ka hukm deti hai aur agar hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat mubaraka ko lein to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) halal nahin huye they yahan tak ke qurbaaniyaan zibeh ho gaeen."
2744,Hazrat Muhammad (Baaqar) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey marwi hai ke hum Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye aur hamney un sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Haj key barey mein puchha to unhoney bayan farmaya ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yamen sey qurbani key janwer ley kar aaye aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Madina Munawra sey qurbani key janwer ley kar aaye. aap ney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : tum ney kya ehraam baandha hai? unhoney kaha : mainey kaha hai : main ehraam baandhta hun Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ehraam ki tarah. aur merey sath qurbani key janwer bhi hain. aap ney farmaya : phir tum ( Umra kar key) halal na hona.
2745,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yamen ki hukmrani sey farigh ho kar aaye to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Ali! tum ney kya ehraam baandha hai? unhoney kaha : jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ehraam baandha hai. aap ney farmaya : qurbani key janwer ( qurbani waley din ) zibeh karna aur us waqt tak ehram ki halat mein raho jaisey ke tum ho. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) apney liye qurbani key janwer laye they.
2746,"Hazrat Baraa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yamen par haakim muqarrar farmaya to main bhi unkey sath tha. mujhey bhi unkey sath kuch oqiye miley they, phir jab Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas (Yamen sey Hajjatul-wadaa mein Makka) aaye to Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey dekha ke Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney ghar ko khushbu laga rakhi thi. main (Hazrat Fatima ki taraf tawajjoh kiye baghair ) ghar sey guzar gaya to wo mujhey kehney lagen : kya wajeh hai? (aap tawajjoh nahin farma rahey ) ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney sahaba ko khud hukm diya hai aur wo halal ho chukey hain. mainey kaha : mainey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ehraam ki tarah ehraam baandha hai, phir main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya. aap ney farmaya : tum ney kaisey ehraam baandha hai? mainey kaha : mainey aap key ehraam ki tarah baandha hai. aap ney farmaya : main qurbani key janwer sath laya hun aur mainey Haj aur Umerey ka ikhatta ehraam baandha hai."
2747,"Hazrat Naafey sey manqul hai ke jis saal hujjaaj ney Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) par hamla kya to Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney us saal ka Haj ka irada farmaya. un sey kaha gaya ke un ( hujjaaj aur ibn Zuber ) key darmiyan ladaai hogi aur khatra hai ke log aap ko baitullah sey roken. unhoney farmaya : ( Quran mein hai : ) yaqinan tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key tarze-amal mein behtareen namoona hai. aisi surat mein main is tarah karunga jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (suleh Hudebia key zamaney mein) kya tha. main tumhein gawah banata hun ke mainey Umerey ka ehraam baandh kar usey apney aap par wajib kar liya hai, phir wo nikley yahan tak ke jab wo beda (maqam) par pahunchey to kehney lagey : Haj aur Umerey ka maamla (agar main baitullah tak na pahunch saka) to eik hi hai, lihaza mein tumhein gawah banata hun ke mainey apney Umerey key sath Haj bhi wajib kar liya hai (yani ehraam mein Haj ko bhi dakhil kar liya hai). phir unhoney qurbani ka janwer bhi sath ley liya jo unhoney Quded sey kharid tha, phir wo dono (hajj o umrah) ki labbaik kehtey huye chaley yahan tak ke Makka Mukarrama pahunch gaey. baitullah ka tawaf kya. Safa Marwa ki saee ki aur us sey zayed kuch na kya. (us waqt) na qurbani ki, na sar mundwaya, na baal katwaaey aur na kisi haram chiz sey halal huye yahan tak ke qurbaniyon ka din aa gaya, phir unhoney qurbani zibeh ki aur sar mundwaya aur unhoney ye khayal kya ke unhoney pehley tawaf key sath apney Haj o Umerey ka tawaf mukammal kar liya hai. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aisey hi kya tha."
2748,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko labbaik kehtey suna. aap farma rahey they : ( لَبَّیْکَ اللّٰھُمَّ ! لَبَّیْکَ … لَا شَرِیْکَ لَکَ ) main hazir hun. aey Allah! main hazir hun. main hazir hun. tera koi shareek nahin. main hazir hun. bilashuba tamam tareefein aur ehsanat terey sath khas hain aur hukumat bhi teri hai. tera koi shareek nahin. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Zul-Hulefa mein do rakatein padhtey they, phir jab oontni Zul-Hulefa ki masjid mein aap ko ley kar khadi hoti to aap buland aawaz sey ye kalmaat ada farmatey."
2749,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) yun labbaik kehtey they : ( لَبَّیْکَ اللّٰھُمَّ ! لَبَّیْکَ … لَا شَرِیْکَ لَکَ ) main hazir hun. aey Allah! main hazir hun. bar-bar hazir hun. tera koi shareek nahin. main hazir hun. yaqinan tamam tareefein aur ehsanat terey sath hi khas hain aur hukumat bhi teri hi hai. tera koi shareek nahin.
2750,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki labbaik is tarah thi : ( لَبَّیْکَ اللّٰھُمَّ ! لَبَّیْکَ … لَا شَرِیْکَ لَکَ ) main hazir hun. aey Allah ! main hazir hun. bar-bar hazir hun. tera koi shareek nahin. main hazir hun. yaqinan tamam tareefen terey liye hain aur inaamat terey sath khas hain aur hukumat bhi teri hi hai. tera koi shareek nahin.
2751,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki labbaik is tarah thi : (لَبَّیْکَ اللّٰھُمَّ ! لَبَّیْکَ … لَا شَرِیْکَ لَکَ),''hazir hun. aey Allah ! main hazir hun. main hazir hun. tera koi shareek nahin. main hazir hun. bilashuba tamam tareef aur ehsanat terey sath khas hain aur hukumat bhi. tera koi shareek nahin.'' Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney is mein ye alfaz (apni taraf sey) badhaey : (لَبَّیْکَ وَ سَعْدَیْکَ , وَالْخَیْرُ فِی یَدَیْکَ , وَالرَّغْبَاءُ اِلَیْکَ وَالْعَمَلُ),''hazir hun, hazir hun aur apney aap ko terey huzur pesh karta hun. har qism ki bhalai terey hi haathon mein hai. hamara maangna bhi tujhi sey hai aur amal bhi terey hi liye hai.''"
2752,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki labbaik yun thi : (لَبَّیْکَ اللّٰھُمَّ ! لَبَّیْکَ … اِنَّ الْحَمْدَ وَالنَّعْمَۃَ لَکَ), ''hazir hun. aey Allah ! main hazir hun. bar-bar hazir hun. tera koi shareek nahin. hazir hun. yaqinan tamam tareefen aur inaamat terey liye khas hain.''"
2753,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki labbaik ye thi : (لَبّیْکَ اِلٰہَ الْحَقِّ),''main hazir hun aey mabood bar-haq.''Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke main nahin janta ke is riwayat ko Abdul-Azeez key ilawa kisi aur ney Abdullah bin Fazal sey marfooa muttasil bayan kiya ho, balke Ismail bin Umayya ney un sey ye riwayat mursal bayan ki hai. (goya Imam Nasai Abdul-Azeez ki riwayat ko durust nahin samajh rahey.)"
2754,"Hazrat Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey paas Jibril alehissalam aaye aur kehney lagey : aey Muhammad ! apney sathiyon ko hukm den ke labbaik buland aawaz sey kahen."
2755,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz key baad talbiya pukara."
2756,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Zohar ki namaz bedaa mein padhi, phir sawar huye aur bedaa key pahad par chadhey aur jab Zohar ki namaz padhi thi, usi waqt Haj aur Umerey ki labbaik kahi thi."
2757,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Hajjatul-wadaa key barey mein riwayat hai ke jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Zul-Hulefa mein tashrif laye to aap ney namaz padhi. aap (labbaik sey) khamosh rahey yahan tak ke aap bedaa mein pahunchey.
2758,Hazrat Salim ney apney walid (Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ko farmatey suna ke ye tumhari bedaa hai jiski baabat tum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par jhoot boltey (ghalat bayaani kartey) ho. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Zul-Hulefa ki masjid sey labbaik keh liya tha.
2759,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap Zul-Hulefa mein apni sawari par sawar hotey they, phir sawari aap ko ley kar khadi hoti to aap labbaik farmatey."
2760,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan farmaya kartey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us waqt labbaik kehtey jab aap ki sawari aap ko ley kar khadi hoti.
2761,Hazrat Ubaid bin Juraij bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey arz kiya ke mainey aap ko dekha hai aap us waqt labbaik kehtey hain jab sawari aap ko ley kar khadi hoti hai (kya wajeh hai?) unhoney farmaya : bilashuba Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi isi waqt labbaik farmaya kartey they jab aap ki sawari aap ko ley kar uthti aur sidhi khadi ho jati.
2762,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (Madina Munawra mein) nau saal thehrey magar aap ney Haj nahin farmaya, phir (daswen saal mein) aap ney tamam logon mein Haj ka aelan farmaya. koi aisa shakhs baqi na raha jo sawar ya pedal aaney ki taqat rakhta tha magar wo na aaya ho (yani zarur aaya). sab log jama ho gaey taake aap key sath Haj ko jaeyn yahan tak ke Zul-Hulefa mein pahunchey to Hazrat Asma binte Umes (Raziallahu anhu) ney Muhammad bin Abi Bakar ko janm diya. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pegham bheja to aap ney farmaya : to ghusl kar key langot baandh ley, phir labbaik shuru kar dey. chunanche unhoney aisey hi kiya. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai."
2763,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Asma bint Umes (Raziallahu anhu) ney (Hajjatul-wadaa key moqey par Zul-Hulefa mein) Muhammad bin Abi Bakar ko janm diya to unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pegham bheja, wo aap sey poochh rahi thin ke ab kya kerey? aap ney unhein hukm diya ke ghusl kar key langot baandh ley aur labbaik kahe (yani ehraam shuru kar dey)."
2764,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke hum (Hajjatul-wadaa key moqey par) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath sirf Haj ka ehraam baandhey (ya Haj ki labbaik kehtey huye) ja rahey they lekin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney umerey ka ehraam baandh rakha tha. jab hum sarf maqam par pahunchey to unhein haiz shuru ho gaya yahan tak ke jab hum (Makka Mukarrama mein) aaye to hamney baitullah ka tawaf kiya aur Safa-Marwa ki saee ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein hukm diya ke jo shakhs apney sath qurbani ka janwer nahin laya, wo halal ho jaey. hamney kaha : kis qisam key halal hon? aap ney farmaya : mukammal halal ho jaeyn. chunanche hamney apni biwiyon sey jima kiye, khushbuein lagaeen aur aam kapdey pehney, halanke hamarey aur youme-arfa key darmiyan sirf chaar raaten baqi thin, phir hamney tarwiye (8 Zul-hijja) key din dobara ehraam baandha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas aaye to unhein rotey huye paya. aap ney farmaya : tujhey kya huwa? unhoney kaha : huwa ye hai ke mujhey haiz aa raha hai. log (umrah kar key) halal ho gaey hain aur main halal nahin ho saki (yani Umra hi nahin kar sakii). ab log Haj ko ja rahey hain. aap ney farmaya : (koi baat nahin) ye chiz to Allah Taala ney Adam ki betiyon par likh rakhi hai, lihaza to ghusl kar, phir Haj ka ehraam baandh ley. to unhoney aisey hi kiya aur tamam theherney ki jagahon (Mina, Arafat aur Muzdalfa) main thehren yahan tak ke jab wo haiz sey paak ho gaeen to unhoney baitullah ka tawaf kiya aur Safa, Marwa ki saee ki, phir aap ney farmaya : to apney Haj aur umerey dono sey halal (farigh) ho gaee hai. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehney lagin : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney dil mein kuchh mehsus kar rahi hun kyonkey mainey Haj sey qabl baitullah ka tawaf waghera nahin kiya. aap ney farmaya : aey Abdur-Rehman ! inhein ley jao aur inhein Tan'eem sey Umra karao. ye us raat ki baat hai jo aap ney mohsib mein guzari thi."
2765,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Hajjatul-wadaa mein nikley to hamney Umerey ka ehraam baandha, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs key sath qurbani ka janwer hai, wo Umerey key sath Haj ka ehraam bhi baandh ley, phir wo halal na ho yahan tak ke dono sey halal ho. main Makka mein aai to mujhey haiz aa raha tha. (haiz ki bina par) mainey baitullah ka tawaf kya na Safa Marwa key darmiyan saee ki. mainey is baat ki shikayat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ki to aap ney farmaya : apna sar (yani baal) khol lo aur kanghi karo aur Haj ka ehraam baandh lo aur Umra chhod do. mainey aisey hi kya. jab mainey Haj pura kar liya to mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ( merey bhai ) Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key hamraah Taneem ki taraf bheja, to mainey Umra kya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye terey us Umerey ki jagah hai (jo tujh sey reh gaya tha). to jinhoney sirf Umerey ka ehraam baandha tha, unhoney baitullah ka tawaf kya aur Safa Marwa key darmiyan saee ki, phir wo halal ho gaey, phir unhoney Mina sey wapis aaney key baad apney Haj ka eik aur tawaf kya lekin jinhoney Haj aur Umerey ka ikhatta ehraam baandha tha, unhoney sirf eik tawaf kya."
2766,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Zabaa (Raziallahu anhu) ney Haj ka irada kya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein hukm diya ke wo (ehraam key waqt ) shart laga lein to unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey aisey hi kya.
2767,"Hazrat Hilal bin Khubab ney kaha : mainey Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey aadmi key ehraam Haj mein shart laganey key barey mein puchha to wo kehney lagey : shart to logon key darmiyan hoti hai (na ke Allah Taala key sath). to mainey unhein Hazrat ikrima wali riwayat bayan ki jo unhoney mujhey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan ki thi ke Hazrat Zaba bint Zuber bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ayen aur kehney lagin : aey Allah key Rasool! main Haj ka irada rakhti hun to main kaisey kahun? aap ney farmaya : to (ehraam key waqt) keh : main hazir hun aey Allah ! main hazir hun. merey halal honey ki jagah wo hogi jahan to mujhey rok ley. (yani jahan bimari mujhey aajiz kar dey.) phir jo to apney rab sey shart lagaeygi, tujhey is par amal karney ka haq hoga."
2768,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Zabaa bint Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aain aur kehney lagin : aey Allah key Rasool ! main bimar aurat hun aur Haj ka irada rakhti hun to aap mujhey kis tarah ehraam baandhney ka hukm detey hain? aap ney farmaya : ehraam baandh lo aur shart laga lo ke merey halal honey ki jagah wo hogi jahan (aey Allah ! ) to mujhey rok lega .
2769,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Zabaa (Raziallahu anhu) key paas tashrif ley gaey to wo kehney lagen : aey Allah key Rasool ! main bimar hun aur main Haj ka irada bhi rakhti hun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : tum Haj ko jao lekin shart laga lo ke main wahan halal ho jaungi jahan to mujhey rok lega. Is-haq bin Ibrahim farmatey hain : mainey (apney ustaad ) abdur-Razzaaq sey puchha : kya Hisham aur Zohri dono Hazrat Aaisha ka naam letey hain? unhoney farmaya : haan. abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) bayan kartey hain ke main nahin janta ke ye riwayat Maamar key ilawa kisi ney Zohri sey muttasil marfoo bayan ki ho. (magar us sey Maamar ki riwayat kamzor nahin banti kyonkey Maamar bazaate-khud qabile-bharosa raawi hain.)
2770,Hazrat Salim bayan kartey hain ke ( walid mohtaram ) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ehraam Haj mein shart laganey ka inkar farmatey they aur kehtey they : kya tumhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat kafi nahin ? agar tum mein sey koi shakhs Haj sey rok diya jaey to wo baitullah ka tawaf karey aur Safa Marwa key darmiyan saee kerey. phir wo har chiz sey ( jo ehraam mein mamnoo thi ) halal ho jaey yahan tak ke aainda saal Haj karey aur janwer bhi zibeh kerey. aur agar janwer na paey to rozey rakhey.
2771,"Hazrat Salim apney walid ( ibne-Umar ) key barey mein bayan farmatey hain ke wo Haj key ehraam mein shart laganey ka inkar kya kartey they aur farmatey they : kya tumhein tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat kafi nahin ? ke aap ney shart nahin lagai. agar tum mein sey kisi ko koi rukawat pesh aa jaey to (jab moqey miley) baitullah aaye, us ka tawaf kerey. Safa Marwa key darmiyan saee kerey. phir sar mundwaaey ya baal katwaa ley, phir halal ho jaey aur is par aainda saal Haj hoga."
2772,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima aur Marwan bin Hakam sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Umra Hudebiya key waqt eik hazar aur chand so sahaba key sath ( Madina Munawra sey) nikley, yahan tak ke jab wo Zul-Hulefa mein pahunchey to aap ney qurbani key oonton ko qaladey daley aur ashaar kya aur Umerey ka ehraam baandha, ye riwayat mukhtasar hai."
2773,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima aur Marwan bin Hakam sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Umra Hudebiya key waqt eik hazar aur chand so sahaba key sath (Madina Munawra sey) nikley, yahan tak ke jab wo Zul-Hulefa mein pahunchey to aap ney qurbani key oonton ko qaladey daley aur ashaar kya aur Umerey ka ehraam baandha, ye riwayat mukhtasar hai."
2774,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney qurbani key oonton ko ashaar kya.
2775,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney oonton ko daeyn janib zakham lagaya, phir us sey khoon ponchha is tarah aap ney ashaar kya."
2776,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Zul-Hulefa mein pahunchey to aap ney apni oontni key barey mein hukm diya to uski kohaan ki daain janib ashaar kya gaya, phir aap ney us sey khoon ponchha aur do jootey (rassi mein dal kar) uskey galey mein latka diye. jab oontni aap ko ley kar beda par chadhi to aap ney buland aawaz sey labbaik kaha."
2777,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Madina Munawra sey qurbani key janwer Makka Mukarrama ko bheja kartey they. mein aap key qurbani key janweron key qaladey ( rassiyan ) bati thi, phir aap un chizon sey perhez nahin farmatey they jin sey eik Mohrim perhez karta hai."
2778,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key qurbani key janweron key liye qaladey tayyar karti thi, phir aap unhein (Haram key liye) bhej detey, phir wo sab kaam kartey jo eik halal shakhs karta hai, halanke wo janwer abhi tak apni jagah nahin pahunchey hotey they."
2779,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke yaqinan main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Haram ko bhejey janey waley janweron key qaladey tayyar karti thi, phir (unhein bhejney key baad) aap Madina Munawra hi mein thehertey aur Mohrim nahin bantey they."
2780,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key qurbani key janweron key liye qaladey bat'ti (tayyar kya karti) thi. aap wo qaladey un janweron ko pehnatey, phir unhein Haram key liye bhej kar khud Madina Munawra hi mein rehtey aur kisi aisi chiz sey ijtinab nahin farmatey they jis sey Mohrim ijtinab karta hai."
2781,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai, farmati hain ke mujhey achi tarah yad hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki Haram ko bheji janey wali bakriyon key liye qaladey tayyar karti thi, phir aap (unhein Haram ki taraf bhejney key baad) halal rehtey."
2782,"Hazrat ummul-Mominin (Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha)) ney farmaya : mainey wo qaladey oon sey batey they jo hamarey paas thi, phir aap ( qaladey waley janweron ko Haram bhejney key baad ) hum mein rahey. wo tamam kaam kartey they jo eik halal shakhs ya aam aadmi apni biwi key sath karta hai."
2783,"Hazrat Hafsa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (Raziallahu anha) ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya wajeh hai ke log to Umra kar key halal ho gaey hain magar aap apney Umerey sey halal nahin huye ? aap ney farmaya : mainey apney sar ko gond lagai hai aur janweron ko qaladey daley hain, lihaza mein halal nahin hunga yahan tak ke main janwer zibeh karun."
2784,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Zul-Hulefa pahunchey to aap ney qurbani key janwer ki kohaan ki daeyn janib ashaar kya, phir us sey khoon door farmaya aur do jootay uskey galey mein latkaaey, phir apni oontni par sawar huye. jab wo aapko ley kar beda par chadhi to aap ney labbaik kaha aur Zohar ki namaz key waqt ehram baandha. aur Haj ka labbaik pukara."
2785,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key qurbani waley oonton key qaladey apney haathon sey batey, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wo qaladey unkey galon mein latkaaey aur unhein ashaar kya aur unhein baitullah ki taraf bheja magar khud ( Madina Munawra mein) tashrif farma rahey. aap par koi aisi chiz haram na hui jo pehley halal thi. ( yani aap par ehraam ki pabandiyan laagu na huin. )"
2786,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key qurbani waley oonton key qaladey tayyar kiye, phir aap ( unhein Haram mein bhejney key bawajud ) na to Mohrim baney aur na kisi qism key kapdey pehney tarak kiye (jo Mohrim ko tarak karney padtey hain )."
2787,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key qurbani waley janweron key qaladey tayyar kya karti thi jabkey wo janwer bakrey bakriyan they.
2788,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bakriyan bhi Haram ko bheja kartey they.
2789,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik dafa bakriyan Haram ko bhejin aur unhein qaladey daley.
2790,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki qurbani ki bakriyon key qaladey tayyar kya karti thi, phir ( unhein Haram mein bhejney key bawajood) aap Mohrim nahin hotey they."
2791,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki qurbani (ki Haram) wali bakriyon key liye qaladey bataa karti thi, phir aap unhein Haram ki taraf bhejney key baad) Mohrim nahin hotey they."
2792,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hum bakriyon ko qaladey dala kartey they, phir unhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Haram ki taraf bhejtey they aur khud ( Madina Munawra mein) halal rehtey they. aap par koi chiz haram na hoti thi."
2793,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Zul-Hulefa pahunchey to aap ney qurbani key oont ko kohaan ki daeyn janib ashaar kya, phir us sey khoon door kya, phir aap ney usey do jootay galey mein daley, phir apni oontni par sawar huey. jab wo aap ko ley kar bedaa par chadhi to aap ney Haj ka labbaik kaha aur Zohar ki namaz key waqt ehraam baandha. aur Haj ka labbaik pukara."
2794,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke jab sahaba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Madina Munawra mein hotey they to wo (kabhi-kabhi) qurbani key janwer Haram ko bhejtey they. phir jo chahta ehraam baandh leta, jo na chahta na baandhta."
2795,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key qurbani key janwaron key qaladey apney haathon sey bata karti thi, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney daste-mubarak sey wo qaladey unkey galon mein daltey they, phir unhein merey walid mohtaram key sath Haram ki taraf bhejtey they, phir aap koi aisi chiz tarak nahin farmatey they jisey Allah Taala ney aap key liye halal kar rakha tha. aap qurbani ka janwer zibeh honey ka intizar nahin farmatey they."
2796,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Haram janey waley janweron key liye qaladey bata karti thi, phir aap kisi aisi chiz sey perhez nahin farmatey they jin sey Mohrim perhez karta hai."
2797,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Haram ko janey waley qurbani key janweron key qaladey khud bata karti thi to aap (unhein Haram bhejney key baad) kisi chiz sey ijtinab nahin farmatey they. farmati hain : hamen malum hai ke haji ko baitullah ka tawaf hi halal karta hai.
2798,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : bilashuba mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key qurbani key Haram janey waley janweron key qaladey khud bata karti thi, phir unhein qaladey dal kar Haram ki taraf rawana kya jata jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ( Madina Munawra hi mein) muqeem rehtey they aur apni aurton (key sath jima) sey perhez nahin farmatey they."
2799,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mujhey achi tarah yad hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki qurbaniyon, yani bakriyon key liye qaladey bata karti thi, phir aap unhein Haram ki taraf bhejtey, phir hum mein halal shakhs ki tarah rehtey they."
2800,Hazrat Muhammad ( Baaqar ) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey marwi hai ke mainey Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huye suna ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Hajjatul-wadaa mein apney qurbani key janweron ko haank kar ley gaey.
2801,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik shakhs ko dekha ke wo qurbani key oont ko haank kar ley ja raha tha (aur khud peechey pedal chal raha tha.) aap ney farmaya is par sawar ho ja. us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! ye qurbani ka oont hai. aap ney farmaya : sawar ho ja tujh par afsos! padhi. ye aap ney dusri ya teesri dafa farmaya.
2802,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko dekha ke wo pedal eik oont ko haankta ley ja raha hai. aap ney farmaya is par sawar ho ja. us ney kaha : ye qurbani ka oont hai. aap ney farmaya : to sawar ho ja. us ney phir kaha : ye qurbani ka oont hai. aap ney chauthi dafa farmaya is par sawar ho ja. tujh par afsos !
2803,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko dekha jo qurbani ka janwer haank kar ley ja raha tha. wo bechara badi mashaqqat sey chal raha tha. aap ney farmaya is oont par sawar ho ja. us ney kaha : ye qurbani ka oont hai. aap ney farmaya : sawar ho ja agar-che ye qurbani ka hai.
2804,"Hazrat abu-Zubair bayan kartey hain ke merey samney Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey qurbani key oont par sawar honey key barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna is par achchey tareeqey sey sawari kar, jab tujhey zarurat pesh aai yahan tak ke tujhey sawari mil jaey."
2805,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hum (Hajjatul-wadaa mein Madina Munawra sey) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath chaley hamari niyat sirf Haj ki thi. jab hum Makka Mukarrama pahunchey to hamney baitullah ka tawaf kya (aur Safa Marwa key darmiyan saee ki ). Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un logon ko jinkey sath qurbani key janwer nahin they, hukm diya ke wo halal ho jaeyn. to jo shakhs qurbani sath nahin laye they, wo halal ho gaey. aap ki biwiyan bhi qurbani key janwer sath nahin laee thin, wo bhi halal ho gaeen. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mujhey to haiz aaney laga tha, lihaza mein baitullah ka tawaf nahin kar saki thi. jab Mohsib wali raat (chaudahwin) hui to mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! log Haj aur Umra kar key (apney gharon ko) jaeyngey aur main sirf Haj kar key jaungi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab hum Makka Mukarrama aaye they to tum ney un raaton mein tawaf nahin kya tha? padhi. mainey kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : apney bhai (Hazrat Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu)) key sath taneem key maqam par jao aur Umerey ka ehraam baandho, phir (Umerey ki adaeygi key baad) hamen falan maqam par aa milna."
2806,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath ( Hajjatul-wadaa mein) nikley to hamara irada Haj hi ka tha. jab hum Makka Mukarrama sey qarib huye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya : jis shakhs key paas qurbani ka janwer hai, wo ( tawaf karney key baad ) apney ehraam par qaaim rahey aur jis shakhs key sath qurbani ka janwer nahin, wo ( Umra karney key baad ) halal ho jaey."
2807,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum ney, yani Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahaba ney khalis Haj ka ehraam baandha tha. kisi aur chiz ki niyat nahin thi. sirf Haj ki niyat thi. hum zul-hijja ki chaar taareekh ki subh ko Makka Mukarrama aaye to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen hukm diya is ehraam ko Umra bana lo aur (umrah kar key) halal ho jao. aap ko ye baat pahunchi ke hum keh rahey hain : jab hamarey aur youme-arfa key darmiyan sirf paanch din ka fasla reh gaya hai to aap hamen halal honey ka hukm dey rahey hain. hum Mina ko jaeyngey to goya hamarey aazaaey-tanasul mani baha rahey hongey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye aur khutba irshad farmaya : jo baat tum ney kahi hai, wo mujhey pahunch gaey hai. yaqinan main tum sab sey badh kar nek aur perhezgar hun aur agar merey sath qurbani key janwer na hotey to main khud halal ho jata. aur agar mujhey is baat ka pehley pata chal jata jiska baad mein pata chala to main qurbani key janwer sath na lata. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yamen sey aaye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney puchha : tum ney kya ehraam baandha hai? unhoney kaha : jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney baandha hai. aap ney farmaya : phir tum ( youm nahar ko) janwer zibeh karna. aur tum Mohrim raho jis tarah tum ho. Hazrat Suraqa bin Malik bin Jaasham ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap farmaain : kya us hamarey Umerey ki ijazat sirf us saal key liye hai ya hamesha key liye ? aap ney farmaya : hamesha key liye."
2808,"Hazrat Suraqa bin Malik bin Jaasham (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap farmaeyn, kya hamara ye Umra ( yani Haj key dinon key doran mein) sirf isi saal key liye hai ya hamesha key liye ? aap ney farmaya : hamesha key liye."
2809,"Hazrat Suraqa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tamatto kya aur hamney bhi aap key sath tamatto kya, phir hamney kaha : kya ye hamarey liye khas hai ya hamesha key liye hai? aap ney farmaya : balke hamesha key liye hai."
2810,Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya Haj ko fasakh kar key Umra banana sirf hamarey liye hai ya sab logon key liye ? aap ney farmaya : balke sirf hamarey liye hai.
2811,Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey tamatto key barey mein manqul hai ke ye sirf hamarey liye rukhsat thi.
2812,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ney tamatto key barey mein farmaya ke ye tumharey liye nahin. na tumhara us sey koi talluq hai. ye to sirf hum, yani as-haab Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye rukhsat thi."
2813,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke tamatto, sirf hamarey liye rukhsat thi."
2814,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin abu-Shasha sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat Ibrahim Nakhai aur Hazrat Ibrahim taimi key sath tha. mainey kaha : mera irada hai ke main us saal Haj aur Umra ikhatta karun. Hazrat Ibrahim kehney lagey : agar tera baap zinda hota to wo ye irada na karta, phir unhoney Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ka farman zikr kya ke (ye khususi ) tamatto sirf hamarey liye hi tha."
2815,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke ehale-jahiliyat ye samajhtey they ke Haj key mahinon mein Umra karna zamin par sab sey bada gunah hai. wo Mohrram ko safar bana liya kartey they aur kehtey they : jab oonton ki pusht par lagney waley zakham theek ho jaeyn aur khub oon ug aaye aur safar (Mohrram) guzar jaey, ya unhoney kaha : safar ka mahina shuru ho jaey to phir Umra karney waley key liye Umra halal hota hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (Hajjatul-wadaa mein) aur aap key sahaba chaar zul-hijja ki subah ko Haj ki labbaik kehtey huye Makka Mukarrama pahunchey to aap ney unhein hukm diya ke is Haj key ehraam ko Umra bana lein. ye chiz unkey nazdik badi shaaq thi. (ke wo halal ho jaeyn) to unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kis qisam ka halaal hona? aap ney farmaya : puri hillat (har tarah se halaal hona)."
2816,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Umerey ka ehraam baandha aur aap key sahaba ney Haj ka ehraam baandha tha. aap ney hukm farmaya ke jinkey sath qurbani ka janwer nahin, wo (umrah kar key) halal ho jaaeyn. aur jinkey paas qurbani key janwer nahin they un mein Hazrat Talha bin Ubedullah aur eik aur shakhs shamil they, lihaza wo dono halal ho gaey."
2817,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye Umra hai. hamney (hajj key sath) us ka faeyda uthaya hai, lihaza jis shakhs key paas qurbani ka janwer nahin, wo mukammal taur par halal ho jaey, aur sun lo ke Umra Haj mein dakhil ho gaya hai."
2818,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. yahan tak ke jab wo Makka Mukarrama key raastey mein they to kuchh sathiyon key sath aap sey peechhey reh gaey. wo sathi mohrim they magar wo (Abu-Qatada) mohrim nahin they. unhoney eik jangli gadhaa dekha to wo fauran apney ghodey par sawar huye, phir unhoney apney sathiyon sey kaha ke unhein unka koda pakda den. in logon ney inkar kiya, phir unhoney un sey apna neza manga to unhoney deney sey inkar kar diya. unhoney (khud utar kar) usey (yani koda) uthaya aur phir jangli gadhey ka peechha kiya aur usey qatl kar diya. (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key kuchh sahaba ney us ka gosht kha liya aur kuchh ney inkar kiya, phir jab wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey miley to aap sey uski baabat puchha. aap ney farmaya : ye Allah Taala ki taraf sey ata karda khana tha jo us ney tumhein khaney key liye mohaiyya farmaya tha."
2819,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman Temi sey riwayat hai ke hum Hazrat Talha bin Ubedullah (Raziallahu anhu) key sath they. hum sab mohrim they. unhein eik perindey ka gosht bator tohfa bheja gaya. wo so rahey they. hum mein sey kuchh ney wo gosht kha liya aur kuchh ney perhez kiya. itney mein Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) jaag padey to unhoney un logon ki taeed ki jinhoney gosht khaya tha aur farmaya : hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath usi parindey ka gosht khaya tha.
2820,"Hazrat (Zaid bin Kaab) Behzi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Makka Mukarrama key iraday sey nikley. aap ehraam baandhey huye they yahan tak ke jab wo (log) maqame-rauhaa mein pahunchey to unhoney eik zakhmi jangli gadhaa dekha. is baat ka tazkira Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : usey kuchh na kaho. ho sakta hai usey zakhmi karney wala aa jaey. itney mein wo Behzi bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa gaya jisney usey zakhmi kiya tha. kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! is jangli gadhey ko aap apni marzi key mutabiq istimal farmaiye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko (taqseem karney ka) hukm diya to unhoney usey tamam sathiyon mein taqseem kar diya, phir aap chal padey yahan tak ke jab Ruweisa aur Araj key darmiyan asaaya maqam par pahunchey to eik hiran saaye mein sar jhukaey khada aaram kar raha tha aur us main eik teer ghusa huwa tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko hukm diya : uskey paas khada reh taake koi shakhs usey pareshan na karey yahan tak ke qafila us sey aagey guzar jaey."
2821,Hazrat Saab bin Jassama Laisi (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat main eik jangli gadhaa bator hadiya pesh kiya. aap us waqt Abwa ya Wadaan maqam mein they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wo unhein wapis kar diya. lekin jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney merey chehrey key gham aur afsaus ko dekha farmaya to farmaney lagey : hamney ye sirf is liye tujhey wapis kiya hai ke hum mohrim hain.
2822,Hazrat Saab bin Jassama (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye yahan tak ke jab aap wadaan mein pahunchey to aap ney eik jangli gadhaa (merey paas bator tohfa) dekha. aap ney wo mujhey wapis farma diya aur farmaney lagey : hum mohrim hain. ye shikar nahin kha saktey (kyonkey ye hamarey liye shikar kiya gaya hai).
2823,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : kya aap nahin jantey ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat aaliya mein shikar kiye huye janwer ka eik tukda pesh kya gaya tha jabkey aap mohrim they, lihaza aap ney qubul na farmaya. Hazrat Zaid ney kaha : haan ! (main janta hun)."
2824,"Hazrat Taoos sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye to Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhein yad karwaatey huye kaha ke aap ney mujhey shikar key gosht key barey mein kaisey bataya tha jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ehraam ki haalat mein pesh kiya gaya tha? wo farmaney lagey : han, haan ! eik aadmi ney aap ki khidmat mein shikar shuda janwer key gosht ka tukda pesh kiya tha to aap ney usey wapis farma diya tha, isi ke sath farmaya : hum ye nahin kha saktey. hum mohrim hain."
2825,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Saab bin Jassama (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein jangli gadhey ki eik raan pesh ki jis sey khoon key qatrey gir rahey they. aap us waqt mohrim they aur maqame-qudaid mein thehrey hue they. to aap ney usey wapis farma diya.
2826,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Saab bin Jassama (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko eik jangli gadhaa bator tohfa pesh kya jabkey aap mohrim they, lihaza aap ney wo unhein wapis farma diya."
2827,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abu-Qatada ney kaha ke merey walid Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Hudebiya waley saal gaey. unkey sathiyon ney ehraam baandh rakha tha magar unhoney ehraam nahin baandha tha. (woh kehtey hain ke) main eik dafa apney sathiyon key paas betha tha ke wo eik dusrey ki taraf dekh kar hansney lagey. mainey (idhar-udhar) dekha to mujhey eik jangli gadhaa nazar aaya. mainey neze sey is par waar kiya (aur usey shikar kar liya, is sey pehley) mainey un sey (shikar key silsiley mein) madad talab ki thi to unhoney meri madad karney sey inkar kar diya tha. (kyonkey wo mohrim they) phir hamney us shikar ka gosht khaya. hamein khatra mehsus huwa ke hamein dushman kahin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey munqata' (alag) na kar dey. main apney ghodey ko tez bhagaatey hue Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey (unhein ittiala karney key liye) chala. kabhi main ghodey ko tez bhagaataa tha. aur kabhi aahista chalata tha. (raastey mein) main aadhi raat ko bano ghifaar key eik aadmi ko mila. mainey us sey puchha : tum ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko kahan chhoda hai? us ney kaha : main aap key paas sey chala to aap saqiyaa maqam par qailula farma rahey they. main aap ko ja mila. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aap key sahaba aap ko salam aur dua arz kartey hain. unhein khatra hai ke kahin dushman (un par hamla kar key) unhein aap sey munqata' (kaat) na dey, is liye aap ruk kar unka intizar farmaeyn. aap ney unka intizar farmaya. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey eik jangli gadhaa shikar kiya hai aur merey paas us ka kuchh gosht baqi hai. aap ney logon sey farmaya : khao. halanke wo mohrim they."
2828,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath ghazwaey Hudebiya mein gaya. sab logon ney Umerey ka ehraam baandh liya. mainey na baandha, phir mainey eik jangli gadhaa shikar kiya aur apney mohrim sathiyon ko us ka gosht khilaya, phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur aap ko batlaya ke hamarey paas us ka bacha huwa gosht mojud hai. aap ney (haazirin sey) farmaya : khao. halanke wo mohrim they."
2829,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo ( log ) apney eik safar mein ja rahey they. un mein sey kuchh mohrim they, kuchh ghair mohrim. Abu-Qatada ney kaha ke mainey eik jangli gadhaa dekha to main ghodey par sawar huwa. neza pakda. mainey un sey madad talab ki magar unhoney madad karney sey inkar kar diya. mainey zabardasti un mein sey kisi sey koda chhina aur gadhey par hamla kar diya. mainey usey shikar kar liya. unhoney bhi us sey kha liya, phir unhein dar mehsus huwa (ke kahin ye najaaiz na ho) to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey is barey mein puchha gaya. aap ney farmaya : kya tum ney (shikar ki taraf) ishara kiya tha? kya tum ney koi madad ki thi? unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : kha saktey ho."
2830,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : tumharey liye khushki ka shikar khana halal hai ba-sharte-ke tum ney shikar na kiya ho aur na tumharey liye shikar kiya gaya ho. Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke raawi hadees Amr bin Abi Amr ilmey-hadees mein qawi nahin agar-che Imam Malik ney un sey riwayat li hai.
2831,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch janwer aisey hain ke mohrim key liye unhein qatl kar deney mein koi harj nahin, kawwa, cheel, bichchhu, choohaa aur kaatney wala kutta."
2832,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch janwer aisey hain jinhein mohrim qatl kar sakta hai : saanp, chuha, cheel, safed pet ya pusht wala kawwa aur kaatney wala kutta."
2833,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mohrim ko paanch qisam key janwer qatl karney ki ijazat di hai : kawwa, cheel, chuha, kaatney wala kutta aur bichchhu."
2834,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey marwi hai ke eik aurat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas aai jabkey unkey haath mein tez nauk wali lathi thi. wo poochhney lagi : ye kis liye? farmaya : in chhipkaliyon key liye kyonkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hum sey farmaya ke har janwer Hazrat Ibrahim alehissalam key liye aag bujhaaney mein koshaan tha magar ye chhipkali. chunanche aap ney hamein isey qatl karney ka hukm diya. aur aap ney hamein gharon mein rehney waley bareek saanpon ko qatl karney sey roka, magar do dhaariyon waley aur chhotey sanp ko qatl kiya ja sakta hai. kyonkey ye nazar khatam kar detey hain aur aurton key hamal gira detey hain."
2835,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch janwer aisey hain ke jo shakhs bhi unhein qatl kar dey, (chahey mohrim hi ho), is par koi harj aur gunah nahin : cheel, chuha, kaatney wala kutta, bichchhu aur kawwa."
2836,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum jab mohrim hon to kin janwaron ko qatl kar saktey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch cheezen aisi hain ke unhein qatl karney waley par koi gunah nahin : cheel, kawwa, chuha, bichchhu aur kaatney wala kutta."
2837,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha gaya : mohrim kon sey janwer qatl kar sakta hai? aap ney farmaya : bichchhu, choohey, cheel, kowey aur kaatney waley kuttey ko qatl kar sakta hai?"
2838,"Hazrat Salim key walid mohtaram sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch janwer aisey hain ke agar koi unhein ehraam ki haalat mein ya Haram key andar bhi qatl kar dey to is par koi gunah nahin (aur wo ye hain ) : chuha, cheel, kawwa, bichchhu aur kaatney wala kutta."
2839,Hazrat ibne Abi Ammaar bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey bijju key barey mein puchha to unhoney mujhey uskey khaney ki ijazat batlaai. mainey kaha ke wo bhi shikar hai? unhoney farmaya : haan. mainey kaha : kya aap ney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai? unhoney farmaya : haan.
2840,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey ehraam ki haalat mein shaadi ki.
2841,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) key sath ) ehraam ki haalat mein nikah farmaya.
2842,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey nikah kya to dono ehraam ki haalat mein they.
2843,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey mazkur hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey nikah farmaya to aap mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein) (Haram mein) they.
2844,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey ehraam ki haalat mein nikah farmaya.
2845,Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein) na apna nikah kerey. na nikah ka pegham bhejey aur na kisi dusrey ka nikah kerey.
2846,Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke Mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein) apna nikah karey ya kisi aur ka nikah karey ya nikah ka pegham bhejey.
2847,"Hazrat Nabiya bin Wahab sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Ubedullah bin Maamar ney Hazrat Aban bin Usman ki taraf pegham bheja, wo poochh rahey they ke kya Mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein) nikah kar sakta hai? to Hazrat Aban ney kaha : mujhey Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney irshad farmaya : mohrim na nikah kerey. na nikah ka pegham bhejey."
2848,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ehraam ki haalat mein seengi lagwaai.
2849,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney seengi lagwaai, halanke aap mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein) they."
2850,"Amr bin Dinar (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Ata sey suna, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna, wo farma rahey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ehraam ki haalat mein seengi lagwaai. baad Azan unhon (Amr bin deenar) ney kaha ke mujhey Taoos ney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey khabar di, wo farma rahey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney haalate-ehraam mein seengi lagwaai."
2851,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ehraam ki haalat mein seengi lagwaai kyonkey aap (key paon) ko moch aa gaee thi.
2852,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney moch aa janey ki wajeh sey ehraam ki haalat mein paon mubarak ki pusht par seengi lagwaai.
2853,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Baheena (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Makka Mukarrama key raastey mein lahiye-jamal key maqam par apney sar mubarak key darmiyan seengi lagwaai, halanke aap Mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein) they."
2854,"Hazrat Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath ehraam ki haalat mein they aur unhein sar mein juon ki takleef ho gaee. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey sar mundaaney ka hukm diya aur farmaya : teen din key rozey rakh lo, ya chhe miskin ko do-do mudd ghalla dey-do, ya eik bakri zibeh kar do. in mein sey jo kaam bhi tum karogey tumhein kafi hoga."
2855,"Hazrat Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey ehraam baandha to merey sar mein juein bahut ziyada ho gaeen. ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tak pahunchi to aap merey paas tashrif laye. main us waqt apney sathiyon key liye salan pakka raha tha. aap ney apni ungli mubarak sey merey sar ko chhua, phir farmaya : baal mundwaa do aur chhe miskin par sadqa kar do."
2856,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha ke usey uski oontni ney gira kar uski gardan tod di, jabkey wo Mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein) tha. wo faut ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey pani aur beeri key patton sey ghusl do aur isey iskey (ehraam waley) do kapdon mein kafan dey do. usey khushbu na lagao, na iskey sar ko dhaanpo kyonkey ye qiyamat key din labbaik kehta huwa utheyga."
2857,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein) aadmi apni oontni sey gir pada. uski gardan toot gaee aur wo mar gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey pani aur beeri key patton sey ghusl do aur isey do kapdon mein kafan do. phir iskey baad farmaya : is ka sar nanga rahey aur isey khushbu na lagana kyonkey ye qiyamat key din labbaik padhta utheyga. (raawi hadees) Shoba ney kaha ke mainey das saal baad us (ustaad Abu-Bashar) sey phir ye hadees poochhi to unhoney isi tarah bayan kiya jis tarah (das saal pehley) wo ye hadees bayan kartey they, sirf itna ziyada kaha : uskey sar aur chehrey ko na dhaanpo."
2858,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Arfey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath wuqoof kar raha tha ke wo apni oontni sey gir pada aur us (sawari) ney uski gardan tod dali. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey pani aur beeri key patton sey ghusl do, isey do kapdon mein kafan do, isey Hanoot na lagao aur na is ka sar dhaanpo kyonkey Allah Taala isey uthaeyga to wo labbaik keh raha hoga."
2859,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik Mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein) ko uski oontni ney gira kar maar diya. usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya to aap ney farmaya : isey ghusl aur kafan do magar is ka sar na dhaanpo aur na khushbu lagao, yaqinan ye labbaik kehta huwa utheyga."
2860,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Haj kar raha tha. usey uskey oont ney gira diya aur wo mar gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey ghusl diya jaey, do kapdon mein kafan diya jaey aur iskey sar aur chehrey ko na dhanpa jaey kyonkey ye qiyamat key din labbaik kehta huwa utheyga."
2861,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik Mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein) shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath (hajj ko) aaya. (arafat mein) wo apney oont sey gir pada. uski gardan toot gaee aur wo mar gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey pani aur beeri key patton sey ghusl do aur isey (kafan mein) isi key (ehraam waley) do kapdey pehna do aur is ka sar na dhaanpo kyonkey ye qiyamat key din labbaik kehta huwa aayega.
2862,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abdullah aur Hazrat Salim bin Abdullah ney (apney walid) Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey guftoogu ki, ye us waqt ki baat hai jab (Hujjaaj ka) lashkar Hazrat ibne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ka muhaasra kar chuka tha. abhi unhein shaheed nahin kiya gaya tha. wo dono kehney lagey ke aap is saal Haj ko na jaeyn to aap ko koi nuqsan nahin. hamein khatra hai ke hamein Baitullah tak pahunchney mein rukawat pad jaeygi. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath (umrah karney key liye) gaey they. kuffar Quraish ney Baitullah tak na janey diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni qurbani zibeh ki aur sar mundwaa diya. main tumhein gawah banata hun ke mainey umerey ka ehraam baandh liya hai. Allah Taala ney chaha to main jaunga. agar merey aur Baitullah key darmiyan raasta khula raha to main tawaf (yani umrah) kar lunga aur agar rukawat pad gaee to main wohi kuchh karunga jo mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath kiya tha. phir kuchh der chalney key baad kehney lagey : Umra aur Haj dono ka maamla eik hi hai, lihaza main tumhein gawah banata hun ke mainey apney umerey key sath Haj ka ehraam bhi baandh liya hai. to aap un sey halal nahin huye yahan tak ke qurbaaniyon waley din qurbani zibeh ki aur phir halal huye."
2863,Hazrat Hujjaaj bin Amr Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs (dorane-ehraam mein baitullah tak pahunchney sey pehley) langdaa ho jaey ya uski taang waghera toot jaey (aur us ka Baitullah tak pahunchna mumkin na rahey) to wo halal ho gaya aur is par dobara Haj hoga. (raawi ney kaha : ) mainey is barey mein Hazrat ibne-Abbas aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha to unhoney farmaya ke Hazrat Hujjaaj Ansari ney sach bayan farmaya.
2864,Hazrat Hujjaaj bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ki taang waghera toot jaey ya wo langdaa ho jaey (yahan tak ke wo baitullah tak nahin pahunch sakta) to wo halal ho gaya aur is par aainda Haj hoga. (Ikrima ney kaha : ) mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha to unhoney farmaya ke Hazrat Hujjaaj Ansari ney sach kaha. (ustaad) Shuaib ney apni hadees mein kaha is par aainda saal Haj hoga.
2865,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Makka Mukarrama tashrif latey to maqame- Zi-tuwaa mein raat guzaarey yahan tak ke wahin subah ki namaz padhtey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key wahan namaz padhney ki jagah eik badey sey tiley par thi. us masjid wali jagah mein nahin jo wahan baad mein banai gaee balke us sey kuchh nichey eik sakht tiley par.
2866,"Hazrat Muharrish Ka'bi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke yaqinan Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) maqam Jaarana sey raat key waqt Umra karney key liye nikley aur subah sey pehley wapis Jaarana mein aa gaey. goya ke raat wahin rahey, yahan tak ke jab suraj dhal gaya to aap Jaarana sey nikal kar wadi sarf mein aagey aur sarf sey Madina Munawra ka raasta ikhtiyar farmaya."
2867,"Hazrat Muharrish Ka'bi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Jaarana sey aisi raat mein nikley jo pighli hui chaandi ki tarah safed thi, phir aap ney (Makka Mukarrama pahunch kar) Umra farmaya aur phir subah sey pehley wapis Jaarana mein lot aaye goya ke raat yahin rahey hon."
2868,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) oonchi ghaati sey Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil huye jo Bat'haa key qarib hai aur neechi ghaati sey nikley.
2869,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil huye to aap ka jhandaa safed tha.
2870,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil huye to aap key sar par khud tha. aap sey kaha gaya ke ibne Khatal Kaba key pardon sey latka huwa hai. aap ney farmaya : isey qatl kar do.
2871,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) fateh Makka key saal Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil huye to aap key sar mubarak par khud tha.
2872,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) fateh Makka key din Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil huye to aap ney siyah pagdi baandh rakhi thi aur aap ehraam key baghair they.
2873,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sahaba chaar zul-hijja ki subah ko Haj ki labbaik kehtey huye Makka Mukarrama mein tashrif laye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein hukm diya ke wo (umrah karney key baad) halal ho jaeyn.
2874,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) zul-hijja ki chaar taareekh ko (Makka Mukarrama) tashrif laye. aap ney Haj ka ehraam baandh rakha tha. aap ney subah ki namaz Bat'haa mein padhi aur farmaya : jo shakhs Haj key ehraam ko umerey mein badalna chahey, wo badal dey."
2875,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) zul-hijja ki chaar taareekh ki subah ko Makka Mukarrama tashrif laye.
2876,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Umra qaza key moqey par Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil huye to Abdullah bin Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) aap key aagey aagey chal rahey they aur ye she'r padh rahey they : aey kafiron ki aulad ! aap ka raasta chhod do. aaj hum aap key hukm sey tumhari gardanen maarengey aur aisi zarab lagaeyngey jo khopdiyon ko gardanon sey juda kar deygi aur dost ko dost sey ghafil kar deygi. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : ibne Rawaaha ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney aur Haram pak mein she'r kehtey ho? to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : umr ! padhney do. ye she'r unkey liye teeron ki bauchhaad sey bhi ziyada takleef-deh hain.
2877,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney fateh Makka key din farmaya : is shehar ko Allah Taala ney us din Haram (hurmat wala) qarar diya tha jis din aasmano aur zamin ko paida farmaya tha, lihaza ye Allah Taala key haram qarar deney sey qiyamat key din tak haram raheyga. uskey kaantay daar darkht na kaatey jaeyn. aur iskey kisi janwer ko na bhagaayaa jaey aur yahan ki giri padi chiz ko koi na uthaey magar wo shakhs jo aelan karta rahey. aur is ki ghaas na kaatii jaey. Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney guzarish ki. aey Allah key Rasool ! magar izkhir ko. aap ney farmaya : magar izkhir ko (kaatney ki ijazat hai)."
2878,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney fateh Makka key din irshad farmaya : bilashuba ye shehar haram hai. isey Allah Taala ney haram qarar diya hai. mujh sey pehley kisi key liye us shehar mein ladaai kerni halal na thi aur mujhey bhi aaj din mein thodi der key liye rukhsat (chhoot) di gaee hai. aur ye Allah Taala key haram qarar deney ki bina par (qiyamat tak key liye) haram raheyga.
2879,"Hazrat Abu-Shuraih (Raziallahu anhu) ney (Madina ke  governer) Amr bin Saeed sey kaha, jab wo Makka Mukarrama ki taraf lashkar bhej raha tha : aey Ameer ! mujhey ijazat do ke main tumharey samney wo baat bayan karun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney fateh Makka sey agley din irshad farmaee thi. merey kanon ney wo baat suni, merey dil ney yad rakhi aur meri aakhon ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha jab aap wo baat farma rahey they. aap ney Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa farmaee, phir farmaya : Makka Mukarrama ko Allah Taala ney haram qarar diya hai logon ney nahin. jo aadmi Allah Taala aur youmey-qiyamat par eman rakhta hai, uskey liye ye jayez nahin ke wo wahan khoon-rezi kerey. aur na wahan key kisi darkht ko kaatey. agar koi shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki ladaai ko hujjat bana kar khud rukhsat hasil karey to usey keh do ke Allah Taala ney apney Rasool ko ijazat di thi, tumhein ijazat nahin di hai. aur mujhey bhi is (fatah waley) din mein thodi der key liye ijazat di gaee thi. ab phir ye isi tarah haram ho gaya hai jis tarah is sey pehley tha. har hazir, ghaayeb ko ye baaten pahuncha dey."
2880,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik lashkar Baitullah par hamla karney aayega magar usey maqame-Bbedaa par dhansa diya jaeyga."
2881,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : lashkar baitullah par hamla karney sey baaz nahin ayengey yahan tak ke un mein sey eik lashkar ko dhansa diya jaeyga."
2882,"Hazrat Hafsa binte umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik lashkar Haram Baitullah ki taraf bheja jaeyga. jab wo maqame-bedaa (eik chatiyal aur banjar maidan) main pahunchengey to unkey awwal aur aakhir ko dhansa diya jaeyga aur unkey darmiyan waley bhi nahin bach sakengey. mainey arz kiya : agar un mein koi momin bhi ho? aap ney farmaya : ye ilaaqa unkey liye bhi (qiyamat tak key liye) qabristaan ban jaeyga (aur kafiron key liye azab)."
2883,Ummul-Mominin Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik lashkar Baitullah par hamla karney aayega yahan tak ke jab wo maqam bedaa (eik chatiyal maidan) main hongey to unkey darmiyan waley dhansa diye jaeynge. unkey awwal aur aakhir (ghabrahat mein) eik dusrey ko pukarengey to un sab ko dhansa diya jaeyga aur koi nahin bach sakeyga magar eikka dukka shakhs jo (wahan sey) bhag kar unkey barey mein logon ko bataeyga. eik shakhs ney un (raawi hadees Umayya bin Safwaan) sey kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke tum ney apney dada par jhoot nahin bola aur tumharey dada ki baabat gawahi deta hun ke unhoney Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) par jhoot nahin bola aur Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ki baabat gawahi deta hun ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par jhoot nahin bola.
2884,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch moozi janwer hil aur Haram mein (har jagah) qatl kiye ja saktey hain : kawwa, cheel, kaatney wala kutta, bichchhu aur choohaa."
2885,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch janwer moozi hain, inhein hill aur Haram mein (har jagah) qatl kiya ja sakta hai, saanp, kaatney wala kutta, safed pet ya pusht wala kawwa, cheel aur choohaa."
2886,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Mina mein wadi khaif key maqam par they ke Sura والمرسلات utri. eik sanp nikla. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey qatl kar do. hum uski taraf lapkey lekin wo apney bil mein dakhil ho gaya.
2887,"Hazrat Abu Ubaida key walid (Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ) bayan kartey hain ke hum Arafey ki raat, jo Arfa ke din sey pehley hoti hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath (Mina mein) they ke achcha aap ney eik sanp ki aahat mehsus ki to farmaya : isey maar dalo. lekin wo apney bil mein ghus gaya. hamney bil mein lakdi dakhil ki aur bil ko kuchh ukhaada, phir is mein kuchh khushk shaakhen (ya bhoosa) dal kar aag laga di. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney tumhein uskey shar sey bacha liya aur usey tumharey shar sey bacha liya."
2888,Hazrat Ummey Shareek (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney chhipkali ko qatl karney ka hukm diya.
2889,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chhipkali bhi fasiq janwer hai.
2890,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch (qisam key) janwer fasiq hain. in ko hill mein bhi qatl kiya ja sakta hai aur Haram mein bhi : kaatney wala kutta, kawwa, cheel, bichchhu aur choohaa."
2891,"Ummul-Mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch (qisam key) janwer fasiq hain jinhein Haram mein bhi qatl kiya ja sakta hai : kawwa, cheel, kaatney wala kutta, choohaa aur bichchhu."
2892,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch janwer aisey hain jinhein maar dalney waley par koi harj nahin : bichchhu, kawwa, cheel, choohaa aur kaatney wala kutta."
2893,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch janwer fasiq hain, hill aur Haram (har jagah) main qatl kiye ja saktey hain : cheel, kawwa, chuha, bichchhu aur kaatney wala kutta. Abdur-Razzaaq (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain ke hamarey baaz as-haab ney bataya ke Maamar us riwayat ko Zohri an-Saalim an Abi key tareeq sey bhi bayan kartey hain aur mazkura tareeq sey bhi."
2894,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch janwer fasiq hain jinhein Haram mein bhi qatl kya ja sakta hai : bichchhu, chuha, kawwa, kaatney wala kutta aur cheel."
2895,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Makka Mukarrama ko Allah Taala ney us din hi haram qarar dey diya tha jis din Allah Taala ney aasman aur zamin paida farmaey. ye na mujh sey pehley kisi key liye halal huwa, na merey baad kisi key liye halal hoga, merey liye bhi din key kuch hissey hi mein halal huwa. aur ab ye phir Allah Taala key haram karney key mutabiq qiyamat tak key liye haram hai. is ki ghaas na kaati jaey. iskey darkht na kaatey jaeyn. iskey shikar ko na chheda jaey. is ki gumshuda chiz kisi key liye halal nahin magar jo aelan karta rahey. Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney jo ke eik tajarba kaar shakhs they, khadey ho kar kaha : magar izkhir kyonkey ye hamarey gharon aur qabron key kaam aati hai. aap ney farmaya : (theek hai) magar izkhir."
2896,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) umratul-qazaa key moqey par Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil huye to Hazrat ibne Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) aap key aagey aagey ye she'r padhtey ja rahey they : aey kafiron ki aulad ! aap ka raasta chhod do. aaj hum aap key hukm par tumhein aisi zarab lagaeyngey jo khopdiyon ko gardanon sey juda kar deygi aur dost ko jigri dost sey ghafil kar deygi. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey : aey ibne Rawaaha ! tum Allah Taala key Haram mein aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein ye ashaar kehtey ho? to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : umr ! rehney do. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! is ka kalam unkey liye teeron ki bauchhaad sey bhi ziyada takleef deh hai.
2897,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Makka tashrif laye to bani Haashim key nojawanon ney aap ka istaqbal kiya. aap ney eik ko apney aagey aur eik ko apney peechhey (sawari par) bitha liya.
2898,"Hazrat Muhaajir Makki sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey us aadmi key barey mein puchha gaya jo Baitullah ko dekhta hai, kya wo haath uthaey? wo farmaney lagey : main to nahin samajhta ke yahudiyon key ilawa koi shakhs ye kaam karta ho. hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Haj kiya. hum to aisey nahin kartey they."
2899,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Taariq ki walida mohtarma (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Daar-Yaala key makaan mein (eik makhsus jagah par) pahunchtey to qibley ki taraf munh kartey aur dua kartey.
2900,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : meri masjid (Masjide-Nabwi) main eik namaz padhna dusri masaajid mein hazar namaz padhney sey afzal hai magar Masjide-Haram mein (is sey bhi afzal hai). Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke main nahin janta ke Musa bin Abdullah Juhni key ilawa kisi ney is hadees ko bawaasta Naafey, ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan kiya ho, balke ibne Juraij waghera ney Musa ki mukhalifat ki hai."
2901,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : meri is masjid (Masjide-Nabwi) main eik namaz dusri masaajid mein hazar namaz sey behtar hai, siwaye Masjide-Kaaba key. (ke usey Masjide-Nabwi sey bhi ziyada fazilat hasil hai)."
2902,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri is masjid main eik namaz dusri masaajid mein hazar namaz sey afzal hai, ilawa Kaba Mushrifa key."
2903,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tujhey ilm nahin ke jab teri qom (Quraish) ney Kaabey ki taamir ki to Hazrat Ibrahim alehissalam ki buniyaadon sey kami kar di? mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya aap isey Hazrat Ibrahim alehissalam ki buniyaadon key mutabiq taamir nahin farmaeyngey? aap ney farmaya : agar teri qom ka zamanaey-kufr taza na hota (to main taamir kar deta). Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke agar Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai to mera khayal hai ke hateem ki taraf sey do konon ka istilaam chhodna isi bina par hoga ke Baitullah Hazrat Ibrahim alehissalam ki buniyaadon par nahin banaya gaya.
2904,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar teri qom (Quraish) ka daure kufr taza na hota to main Baitullah ki imarat ko tod kar usey Hazrat Ibrahim alehissalam ki buniyaadon par taamir kar deta aur us ka eik darwaza pichhli janib bana deta kyonkey Quraish ney jab Baitullah taamir kiya to unhoney uski imarat ko chhota kar diya tha."
2905,Ummul-Mominin (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar meri ya teri qom ka daure jahiliyat qarib na hota to main Kaabey ko giraaney ka hukm deta aur uskey do darwazey bana deta. jab Hazrat ibne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko iqtidar mila to unhoney iskey do darwazey bana diye.
2906,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : aey Aaisha ! agar ye baat na hoti ke teri qom ka daure jahiliyat abhi qarib hai to main Kaabey ko giraaney ka hukm deta aur is mein wo hissa bhi dakhil kar deta jo is sey nikal diya gaya hai. aur main is ka darwaza zamin key barabar laga deta aur iskey do darwazey bana deta, eik mashriqi, eik maghribi kyonkey Makka ke Quraish is ki mukammal taamir sey aajiz aagey they (ke unka halal maal khatam ho gaya tha). aur main isey Hazrat Ibrahim alehissalam ki sahih buniyaadon par taamir karta. Hazrat Urwa ney kaha : yehi wajeh hai jisney Hazrat ibn Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko aamada kiya ke Kaabey ko gira kar (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khahish key mutabiq) taamir karen. (raawi hadees) Yazid ney kaha : jab Hazrat ibne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ney Kaabey ko giraya aur phir banaya to main hazir tha. aap ney is mein Hajar ka kuchh hissa dakhil kar diya tha, isi ke saath mainey Hazrat Ibrahim alehissalam ki buniyaden bhi dekhin. wo patthar they oonton ki kohaanon jaisey, jinhein eik dusrey mein phansa diya gaya tha."
2907,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (qiyamat key qarib) do chhoti-chhoti pindliyon wala habshi Baitullah (Kaabey) ko dhaeyga."
2908,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Kaaba-Mushrifa key paas pahunchey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam), Bilal aur Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) Baitullah key andar tashrif ley ja chukey they aur Usman bin Talha (Kaabey key haajib) ney (dakhil ho kar) darwaza band kar diya tha. wo kuchh der tak andar rahey, phir (Usman bin Talha haajib ney) darwaza khola to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif laye. main seedhi par chadh kar Baitullah mein dakhil ho gaya aur mainey puchha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kahan namaz padhi hai? unhoney kaha : yahan, albatta mein un sey ye poochhnaa bhool gaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Baitullah mein kitni rakaat padhi hain."
2909,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Baitullah mein dakhil huye. aap key sath Fazal bin Abbas, Usama bin Zaid, Usman bin Talha aur Bilal Raziallahu anhum bhi they. unhoney andar sey darwaza band kar liya. aap Baitullah mein thehrey jab tak Allah Taala ney chaha, phir bahar tashrif laye. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main sab sey pehley Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey mila. mainey kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kahan namaz padhi? unhoney farmaya : (agli saf key baain janib waley) do sutonon key darmiyan."
2910,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Baitullah mein dakhil huye. udhar aap key bahar nikalney ka waqt qarib tha. idhar mujhey hajat (zarurat) pesh aa gaee. main qazaey hajat (zarurat se faraghat) key liye gaya aur phir jaldi jaldi wapis aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif la chukey they. mainey Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Kaba Mushrifa mein namaz padhi hai? unhoney farmaya : haan (agli saf key baain janib waley) do sutonon key darmiyan do rakat namaz padhi hai.
2911,Hazrat Mujahid sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ghar mein they ke kisi ney aa kar kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Kaba mein dakhil ho chukey hain. (ibne-Umar ney kaha : ) main aaya to mainey dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif la chukey they aur Bilal abhi darwazey hi par khadey they. mainey kaha : aey Bilal ! kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Kaabey mein namaz padhi hai? wo kehney lagey : haan. mainey kaha : kahan? unhoney kaha : un do sutonon key darmiyan do rakaat padhin phir aap ney bahar tashrif la kar Kaba Mushrifa key darwazey key aen samney do rakatein padhin.
2912,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Kaabey key andar tashrif ley gaey. aap ney Kaabey key atraaf (konon) main tasbeehaat aur takbiraat kahen, namaz nahin padhi, phir aap bahar tashrif laye to maqame Ibrahim key peechhey (Kaaba rukh ho kar) do rakaat padhin phir farmaya : ye qibla hai."
2913,"Hazrat ( Abdullah ) ibne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko farmatey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye baat na hoti ke logon (nau-muslimon) ka daure-kufr abhi taza hai aur merey paas itney ikhrajat bhi nahin jis sey main Baitullah ki taamir asal buniyaadon par kar sakun to main Hajar mein sey paanch haath Baitullah mein dakhil kar deta aur uskey do darwazey banata. eik sey log dakhil hon, dusrey sey niklen."
2914,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ! main Baitullah key andar dakhil na houn? aap ney farmaya : Hajar mein dakhil ho jao. ye Baitullah ka (andruni) hissa hi hai.
2915,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain meri khahish thi ke main Baitullah mein dakhil ho kar namaz padhun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mera haath pakad kar mujhey Hajar mein dakhil kar diya aur farmaya : jab tumhara dil Baitullah mein dakhil honey ko chahey to yahin (Hajar mein) namaz padh liya karo. ye bhi to Baitullah hi ka eik hissa hai, lekin teri qom (Quraish) ney jab Baitullah taamir kiya to isey chhota kar diya."
2916,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Kaabey key andar namaz nahin padhi balke uskey atraaf mein takbeeren kehtey rahey.
2917,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Baitullah mein dakhil huye they. aap ney Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya to unhoney darwaza band kar diya. Baitullah un dino chhe sutonon par qaaim tha. aap (darwazey sey) sidhey gaey yahan tak ke jab un do sutonon key darmiyan pahunchey jo Baitullah key darwazey key samney hain to aap beth gaey, Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa kartey rahey, duayen kartey rahey aur bakhshish talab farmatey rahey, phir aap uthey aur Kaabey ki pichhli deewar (darwazey wali) key muqabil samney wali deewar ki taraf gaey, apna chehra aur rukhsaar deewar sey lagaey aur Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa farmaee, Allah Taala sey duayen maangin aur bakhshish talab farmatey rahey, phir Kaabey key tamam konon mein tashrif ley gaey aur har koney mein takbir, tahleel, tasbih, sanaa, dua aur istighfar farmatey rahey, phir bahar tashrif laye aur Kaabey key darwazey key aen samney do rakaten padhin phir farigh huye to farmaya : ye qibla hai, ye qibla hai."
2918,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Baitullah key andar dakhil huwa. aap beth gaey. Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa aur takbir aur tahleel kartey rahey, phir aap apney samney wali Kaabey ki deewar ki taraf jhukey, apna seena, rukhsaar aur haath is par lagaey, phir takbir aur tahleel kartey rahey. dua maangtey rahey aur ye kaam aap ney tamam konon mein kiya, phir bahar tashrif laye. aap abhi darwazey par they ke qibley ki taraf munh kiya aur farmaya : ye qibla hai, ye qibla hai."
2919,Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Baitullah sey bahar tashrif laye to Kaabey key samney do rakaat padhin phir farmaya : ye qibla hai.
2920,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ney bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Baitullah key andar dakhil huye to uskey tamam atraaf (chaaron konon) main duayen ken, magar namaz nahin padhi yahan tak ke bahar tashrif ley aaye aur Kabey key aen samney do rakaten padhin."
2921,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Saaib Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko pakad kar ley jatey (kyonkey wo na-bina ho gaey they) aur unhein teesrey hissey key paas khada kar detey they jo us rukn key paas hai jo Hajare-Aswad, jo ke darwazey key qarib hai, sey muttasil (laga hua) hai. (yani rukn yamaani key paas). Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey : kya tumhein ye nahin bataya gaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) yahan namaz padha kartey they? wo kehtey they haan, phir aap (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) aagey badhtey aur namaz padhtey."
2922,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubaid bin Umer sey manqul hai ke eik shakhs ney (Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey) kaha : aey Abu-Abdur-Rehman ! main dekhta hun ke aap sirf un do konon (Hajar Aswad aur rukne-yamaani) hi ko chhotey hain (kya wajeh hai?) unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : in do konon ko chhuney sey yaqinan gunah maaf ho jatey hain. isi ke sath mainey aap ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs saat chakkar lagaey, usey ghulam azad karney key barabar sawab milega."
2923,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Kaabey key tawaf key doran main eik shakhs key paas sey guzrey jiski naak mein nakel dal kar eik aur shakhs usey ley ja raha tha. aap ney apney daste-mubarak sey wo nakel (rassi) kaat di aur farmaya : isey haath sey pakad kar chalaao.
2924,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi key paas sey guzrey jisey eik doosra aadmi kisi chiz sey chala raha tha jiski us ney nazar maan rakhi thi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey pakda aur tod diya aur farmaya : ye (ajeeb) nazar hai !
2925,"Hazrat Taoos eik aisey shakhs sey bayan kartey hain jinhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey sohbat ka faayda paya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Baitullah ka tawaf namaz (ki tarah ibadat) hai, lihaza is mein kam hi koi baat karo. ye alfaz Yusuf (bin Saeed) key hain. Hanzala bin Abu-Sufiyaan ney Hasan bin Muslim ki mukhalifat ki hai."
2926,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke tawaf key darmiyan kalam kam karo. (yun samjho) tum namaz mein ho.
2927,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut'im (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Abd Munaaf ki aulad ! tum kisi ko Baitullah key tawaf aur namaz sey na roko jis waqt bhi koi karna chahey, din ho ya raat."
2928,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya ke main bimar hun. aap ney farmaya : tum logon key ooper ooper sey (door sey) sawar ho kar tawaf kar lo. mainey is tarah tawaf kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us waqt baitullah key qarib namaz padha rahey they aur siSoora taur ki tilawat farma rahey they.
2929,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! mainey tawafe-wadaa nahin kiya. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab jamaat shuru ho jaey to tum apney oont par sawar ho kar logon key ooper ooper sey tawaf kar lena. Urwa ney ye Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey nahin suna.
2930,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke wo Makkey mein aayin to bimar thin. unhoney is baat ka zikr Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kiya to aap ney farmaya : tum sawar ho kar namaaziyon key ooper ooper sey tawaf kar lena. mainey (dorane-tawaf) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Kaabey key paas (namaz mein) Sura taur padhtey suna.
2931,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hajjatul-wadaa mein oont par sawar ho kar Kaabey key ird-gird tawaf farmaya aur aap Hajare-Aswad ko apni kham-daar chhadi key sath chhotey they.
2932,"Hazrat Wabra bayan kartey hain ke mainey eik aadmi ko Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey poochhtey suna ke mainey Haj ka ehraam baandha tha, to kya main (hajj ke kaamon sey pehley) tawaf kar sakta hun? unhoney farmaya : tumhein is mein kya rukawat hai? us ney kaha : mainey dekha hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) is sey mana farmatey hain. hamein aap par un sey ziyada aitimad hai (lihaza aap bataeyn). unhoney farmaya : hamney to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai ke aap ney Haj ka ehraam baandha, phir Makka Mukarrama aa kar aap ney Baitullah ka tawaf farmaya aur Safa Marwa key darmiyan saee farmaee."
2933,"Hazrat Amr (bin Deenar) bayan kartey hain ke hamney Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey us shakhs key barey mein puchha jo umerey key ehraam sey aaye, phir Baitullah ka tawaf karey lekin Safa, Marwa key darmiyan saee na karey to kya wo apni biwi sey jima (sambhog) kar sakta hai? unhoney farmaya ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (Makka Mukarrama) tashrif laye they to aap ney Baitullah key saat chakkar lagaey, maqame-Ibrahim key paas do rakaten padhin aur Safa, Marwa key darmiyan saee ki. aur tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (key tarze-amal) main behtareen namoona hai."
2934,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke (Hajjatul-wadaa mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (Madiney sey) chaley hum bhi aap key sath chaley jab aap Zul-Hulefa pahunchey to aap ney Zohar ki namaz padhi, phir apni oontni par sawar huye. jab wo aap ko ley kar bedaa key tiley par chadhi to aap ney Haj aur umerey dono ki labbaik kahi. hamney bhi aap key sath isi tarah labbaik kahi. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Makka Mukarrama tashrif laye aur hamney tawaf kar liya, aap ney logon ko hukm diya ke wo halal ho jaeyn. sab log dar gaey (aur hichkichaey) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar merey sath qurbani ka janwer na hota to main bhi halal ho jata. (ye sun kar) sab halal ho gaey yahan tak ke unhoney apni aurton (biwiyon) sey jima (sambhog) kiya lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) halal nahin huye aur youm nahar (qurbaani ke din) tak baal bhi nahin katwaaey."
2935,"Hazrat Naafey sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Haj aur umerey ka ikhatta ehraam baandha aur eik tawaf kiya, phir farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey kartey dekha hai."
2936,"Hazrat Naafey sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) (Madina Munawra sey Makka Mukarrama key liye) nikley. jab Zul-Hulefa mein pahunchey to umerey ka ehraam baandha. thodi door chaley to unhein khatra huwa ke kahin Baitullah sey rok na diye jaeyn, phir farmaney lagey : agar mujhey rok diya gaya to main wesey hi karunga jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (aisey moqe par) kiya tha, phir farmaney lagey : wallah ! is masley mein Haj aur Umra barabar hi hain. main tumhein gawah banata hun ke mainey apney umerey key sath Haj ka ehraam bhi baandh liya hai, phir chaltey rahey yahan tak ke jab maqame-qudaid mein pahunchey to wahan sey qurbani ka janwer kharida, phir makkey pahunchey to Baitullah key saat chakkar lagaey aur Safa, Marwa key darmiyan saee ki aur farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey kartey dekha hai."
2937,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik tawaf kiya tha.
2938,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Hajare-Aswad jannat sey hai."
2939,"Hazrat Suwed bin Ghafala sey manqul hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hajare-Aswad ko bosa diya aur us sey chimat gaey. farmaney lagey : mainey Hazrat Abul-Qaasim (Rasulullah) (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, tujh sey bahut shafqat aur mohabbat farmatey they."
2940,"Hazrat Aabis bin Rabeea sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke wo Hajare-Aswad key paas aaye aur farmaya : mujhey yaqin hai ke to eik patthar hai aur agar mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko tujhey bosa detey huye na dekha hota to main tujhey bosa na deta, phir uskey qarib huye aur bosa diya."
2941,"Hazrat Hanzala sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke mainey Hazrat Taoos ko Hajare-Aswad key paas sey guzartey dekha. agar aap wahan bheed mehsus farmatey to (ishara kar key) guzar jatey aur bheed na kartey. agar jagah khaali dekhtey to usey teen baar bosa detey, phir farmaya : mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko aisey kartey dekha hai. aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke mainey Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko aisey hi kartey dekha hai, phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : (aey Hajare Aswad ! ) bilashuba to eik patthar hai. na nafa dey sakta hai na nuqsan, agar ye baat na hoti ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko tujhey bosa detey huye dekha hai to main tujhey bosa na deta, phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey hi kartey dekha hai."
2942,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Makka Mukarrama tashrif laye to masjid mein dakhil huye aur Hajare-Aswad ko bosa diya, phir daeyn taraf ko chaley teen chakkar daud kar (kandhey hilaatey huye) chaley aur chaar chakkar aahista chaley, phir maqame-Ibrahim key paas aaye aur ye aayat tilawat farmaai : (وَ اتَّخِذُوْا مِنْ مَّقَامِ اِبْرٰہٖمَ مُصَلًّی) (Sura Baqra 125)  padhi. tum maqame-Ibrahim ko jaey namaz banao. aur do rakaat is tarah padhen ke maqame-Ibrahim aap key aur Baitullah key darmiyan tha. do rakat padhney key baad phir Baitullah key paas gaey aur Hajare-Aswad ko bosa diya, phir Safa ki taraf nikal gaey."
2943,Hazrat Naafey sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) pehley teen chakkaron mein ramal kartey they aur aakhiri chaar chakkaron mein aaram sey chaltey they aur wo farmatey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi aisey hi kiya kartey they.
2944,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Haj aur umerey mein pehla tawaf kartey to teen chakkaron mein tez chaltey aur chaar chakkaron mein aahista chaltey, phir do rakaten padhtey, phir Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan chakkar lagatey."
2945,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Makka Mukarrama pahunchtey to tawaf mein sab sey pehley Hajare-Aswad ko bosa detey. saat mein sey teen chakkaron mein kandhey hila kar tez chaltey.
2946,"Hazrat Naafey sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) jab Haj ya umerey mein aatey to apney (pehley) tawaf mein teen chakkaron mein bhagtey they aur chaar chakkaron mein chaltey they, isi ke saath unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi aisey hi kya kartey they."
2947,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney Hajare-Aswad sey Hajare-Aswad tak ramal farmaya yahan tak ke teen chakkar purey ho gaey.
2948,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sahaba (umratul-qazaa mein) Makka Mukarrama tashrif laye to mushrekin kehney lagey : unhein Yasrib key bukhaar ney kamzor kar diya hai aur un ki haalat bahut patli ho gaee hai. Allah Taala ney apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko is baat ki ittilaa farma di to aap ney apney sahaba ko hukm diya ke wo ramal keren, albatta rukne-yamaani aur Hajare-Aswad key darmiyan aahista chalen kyonkey mushrekin hateem ki janib (Shimaali janib) they. to mushrekin (unhein ramal kartey dekh kar) kehney lagey : ye to bahut ziyada qawi hain."
2949,"Hazrat Zuber bin Adi sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey Hajare-Aswad ko chhuney key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko usey chhotey aur bosa detey dekha hai. wo aadmi kehney laga : farmaiye agar bahut bheed ho aur main be-bas ho jaun to? Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : apna ""farmaiye"" Yamen hi mein rehney dey. mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai ke aap Hajare-Aswad ko chhotey aur bosa detey they."
2950,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har tawaf mein rukne-yamaani aur Hajare-Aswad ko chhotey they.
2951,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Hajare-Aswad aur rukne-yamaani key ilawa kisi koney ko nahin chhotey they.
2952,Hazrat Salim key walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dono yamni konon key ilawa Baitullah key kisi hissey ko chhotey nahin dekha.
2953,Hazrat Ubaid bin Juraij sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : mainey aap ko dekha hai ke aap sirf un do yamni konon (Hajare-Aswad aur rukne-yamaani) hi ko chhotey hain. (kya wajeh hai?) unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko in do konon (rukne-yamaani aur Hajare-Aswad) key ilawa kisi koney ko chhotey nahin dekha. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai.
2954,Hazrat Salim key walid (Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) baitullah key konon mein sey sirf do konon hi ko chhotey they. eik Hajare-Aswad aur doosra uskey sath wala jo (jumahiyyen) key gharon (mohalley) ki taraf hai.
2955,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin Umar) (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab sey mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye do koney, Hajare-Aswad aur rukne-yamaani, chhotey dekha hai mainey kabhi bhi, sakhti ho ya sahulat, un do konon ko chhuna tarak nahin kiya."
2956,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab sey mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Hajare-Aswad ko chhotey dekha hai, mainey shiddat ho ya sahulat, kabhi usey chhuna tarak nahin kiya."
2957,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hajjatul-wadaa mein oont par sawar ho kar tawaf farmaya. aap Hajare-Aswad ko chhadi key sath chhotey they.
2958,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (Hajjatul-wadaa mein) apni sawari par beth kar Baitullah ka tawaf farma rahey they. jab Hajare-Aswad key paas pahunchtey to uski taraf ishara farmatey they.
2959,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke (daure-jahiliyat mein kabhi kabhar) koi aurat nangi Baitullah ka tawaf karti aur yun kehti : aaj (tawaf ki gharaz se) meri kuchh ya puri sharmgah nangi hogi. (aur agar aisa ho to) main kisi key liye is ki taraf nazar karna mabaah (jayaz) qarar nahin deti. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya :  isi bina par ye aayat utri : (یٰبَنِیْٓ اٰدَمَ خُذُوْا . . . . . عِنْدَ کُلِّ مَسْجِدٍ),''aey bani Adam ! har masjid mein jatey waqt zeenat ikhtiyar karo (pura libas pehna karo).''"
2960,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hajjatul-wadaa sey qabl us Haj mein jis mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein Ameerey Haj muqarrar farmaya tha, mujhey kuchh aur logon key sath ye aelan karney key liye bheja ke khabrdar ! is saal key baad koi mushrik Haj karney nahin aayega aur na koi nanga shakhs Baitullah ka tawaf kar sakeyga."
2961,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) key sath aaya jabkey unhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Makkey walon ki taraf sey bara-at (Kaaba ko har tarah ke shirk aur gandagi se paak rakhney) ka aelan karney key liye bheja tha. shagrid ney kaha : aap kya aelan farmatey they? unhoney farmaya : hum aelan kartey they ke momin key ilawa koi shakhs jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga. koi nangaa shakhs Baitullah ka tawaf nahin kar sakeyga. jis shakhs ka Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath suleh ka koi muahida hai to uski muddat chaar maah hai. jab chaar maah guzar jaeyngey to Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mushrekin (key sath har qism key muahidey suleh) sey laa-taaluq hongey aur koi mushrik is saal key baad Haj karney nahin aayega. (Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya :) main ye aelaanat karta raha yahan tak ke meri aawaz beth gaee.
2962,Hazrat Matlab bin Abi Wdaa'a (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha jab aap saatwen chakkar sey farigh huye to aap tawaf wali jagah key (bahir waley) kinarey key paas aagey aur do rakaten padhin (us waqt) tawaf karney walon aur aap key darmiyan koi shakhs (bator sutrah) na tha.
2963,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (Makka Mukarrama) tashrif laye to Baitullah key saat chakkar lagaey. maqame-Ibrahim key peechhey do rakaten padhin aur Safa, Marwa key darmiyan saat chakkar lagaey. phir Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Quran ki aayat tilawat farmaee : (لَقَدْ کَانَ لَکُمْ …),""tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (key tarze-amal) main behtareen namoona hai.''"
2964,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Baitullah key saat chakkar lagaey. un mein sey (pehley) teen chakkaron mein ramal kiya aur chaar chakkaron mein aaram sey chaley, phir maqame-Ibrahim key paas khadey huye. aur do rakaat padhin phir aap ney ye aayat padhi : (وَ اتَّخِذُوْا مِنْ مَّقَامِ اِبْرٰھِیْمَ مُصَلًّی),""tum maqame-Ibrahim ko namaz ki jagah banao.'' aap ney logon ko sunaney key liye ye alfaz buland aawaz sey ada farmaey, phir aap (Hajare-Aswad ki taraf) gaey. usey bosa diya, phir (Safa, Marwa ki taraf) chaley aur farmaya : hum usi jagah sey ibtida (shuruat) kerengey jis ka zikr Allah Taala ney pehley kiya hai. to aap ney koohe-Safa sey ibtida (shuruat) ki. is par chadhey yahan tak ke aap ko Baitullah nazar aaney laga. aap ney teen baar (ye kalimaat ) padhey : (لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللّٰہُ وَحْدَہُ لَا شَرِیْکَ لَہٗ لَہُ الْمُلْکُ … شَیْئٍ قَدِیْرٌ),''Allah key siwa koi (sachha) mabood nahin, wo akela hai, us ka koi shareek nahin, hukumat aur tareef usi ki hai. wohi zindagi deta hai aur maut deta hai aur wo har chiz par khub qadir hai.'' phir aap ney takbeerein kahin aur Allah Taala ki hamd ki, phir aap ney duayen farmaen jo Allah Taala ney aap key liye muqaddar ki thin, phir aap chaltey huye nichey utrey yahan tak ke jab aap key qadam mubarak nasheb (dhaal) mein ja pahunchey to aap daudney lagey yahan tak ke (Marwa ki) chadhai shuru ho gaee to aap aaram sey chalney lagey yahan tak ke Marwa pahunch gaey. to is par chadhtey rahey, phir jab Baitullah nazar aaney laga to aap ney ye kalimaat ada farmaee : (لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللّٰہُ وَحْدَہُ . … شَیْئٍ قَدِیْرٌ), ''Allah key siwa koi mabood (bar-haq) nahin, wo akela hai, us ka koi shareek nahin, badshahi aur tareef usi ki hai aur wo har chiz par qadir hai.'' aap ney ye (kalimaat) teen baar padhey, phir Allah Taala ka zikr kiya aur (Subhan Allah) aur (Alhamdulillah) padhtey rahey, phir aap ney is par duayen farmaeen jo Allah ney chahen (phir) isi tarah kiya yahan tak ke aap (Safa Marwa key) chakkaron sey farigh ho gaey."
2965,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (Baitullah key gird) saat chakkar lagaey. teen mein kandhey hila-kar tez-tez chaley aur chaar mein aaram sey chaley, phir ye aayat padhi : (وَ اتَّخِذُوْا مِنْ مَّقَامِ اِبْرٰھٖیْمَ مُصَلًّی),tum maqame-Ibrahim ko namaz ki jagah banao.'' phir aap ney do rakaat padhin aur maqame-Ibrahim ko apney aur kaabey key darmiyan rakha, phir Hajare-Aswad ko bosa diya, phir nikley aur kaha : Safa aur Marwa Allah Taala ki muqarrar karda alaamaat hain. chunanche wahan sey shuru karo jiska zikr Allah Taala ney pehley farmaya hai (yani saee ka aaghaz Safa sey karo)."
2966,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab maqame-Ibrahim key paas pahunchey to aap ney ye aayat tilawat farmaee : (وَ اتَّخِذُوْا مِنْ مَّقَامِ اِبْرٰھٖیمَ مُصَلًّی),''tum maqame Ibrahim ko namaz ki jagah banao.'' phir aap ney do rakaten padhin aur (un mein) Sura Fatah (key sath) Sura (قُلْ یاَیُّہَا الْکٰفِرُوْنَ) aur sura (قُلْ ھُوَ اللّٰہُ اَحَدٌ) padhin phir aap Hajare-Aswad ki taraf gaey. usey bosa diya, phir kohe-Safa ki taraf nikal gaey."
2967,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zam zam ka pani khadey ho kar piya.
2968,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko zam zam ka pani pilaya. aap ney qiyam ki haalat mein piya.
2969,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Makka tashrif laye to aap ney baitullah key saat chakkar lagaey, phir maqame-Ibrahim ki ot mein do rakaten padhin phir us darwazey sey kohe-Safa key liye nikley jis sey (umuman) nikla jata tha, phir Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan chakkar lagaey. Shoba ney kaha : mujhey Ayub ney ba-wasta Amr bin Dinar ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey khabar di hai ke ye (Safa, Marwa key darmiyan saee) sunnat hai."
2970,"Hazrat Urwa bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key samney ye aayat padhi : (فَلَا جُنَاحَ عَلَیْہِ اَنْ یَّطَّوَّفَ بِہِمَا),us (Haji aur Moa'tamir) par koi harj nahin ke wo Safa, Marwa key darmiyan chakkar lagaey. mainey (is aayat ki roshni mein) kaha : mujhey to koi parwah nahin agar main unkey darmiyan chakkar na lagaaun. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : tu ney bahut ghalat istidlaal kiya. asal baat ye thi ke jahiliyat waley kuchh log Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan chakkar nahin lagatey they. jab Islam (ka daur) aaya aur Quran ki ye aayat utri : (اِنَّ الصَّفَا وَ الْمَرْوَۃَ مِنْ شَعَآئِرِ اللّٰہِ …),''Safa aur Marwa Allah Taala key muqarrar karda nishaanaat hain … الخ.'' to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey chakkar lagaey aur hamney bhi aap key sath chakkar lagaey, lihaza ye sunnat hai."
2971,"Hazrat Urwa bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey Allah Taala key farman : (فَلَا جُنَاحَ عَلَیْہِ اَنْ یَّطَّوَّفَ بِہِمَا),""us (Haji aur Moa'tamir) par koi harj nahin ke wo un dono (Safa aur Marwa) ka tawaf kerey.'' key barey mein puchha ke is sey to malum hota hai ke agar koi Safa aur Marwa ka tawaf na karey to Allah ki qism ! usey koi gunah nahin. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : aey bhaanjey ! tu ney bahut ghalat baat kahi. agar is aayat ka matlab ye hota jo to bayan karta hai to aayat is tarah hoti : (hajj ya umera karney wala) agar wo Safa aur Marwa ka tawaf na karey to usey koi gunah nahin. asal mein baat ye hai ke ye aayat Ansaar key barey mein nazil hui hai. wo Islam laney sey pehley manaat but key naam par ehraam baandhtey they. uski wo puja kartey they. wo mushallal key maqam par nasab (ghada hua) tha. jo log us but key naam par ehraam baandhtey they, wo Safa aur Marwa key chakkar laganey ko gunah samajhtey they, phir (Islam laney key baad) unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey is barey mein puchha to Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaari : (اِنَّ الصَّفَا وَ الْمَرْوَۃَ …),''Safa aur Marwa Allah Taala ki muqarrar karda alaamaat mein sey hain, lihaza jo shakhs Haj ya umerey ka ehraam baandhey to koi harj nahin ke wo unkey chakkar lagaey.''phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey darmiyan chakkar lagana jari farma diya, chunanche ab kisi ko ijazat nahin ke wo un mein chakkar lagana chhod dey."
2972,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna jab aap masjid sey nikal kar Safa, Marwa key tawaf key iradey sey aa rahey they : hum us maqam sey ibtida (shuruat) kerengey jis ka zikr Allah Taala ney pehley farmaya hai."
2973,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kohe-Safa ki taraf nikley aur farmaya : hum us pahadi sey ibtida (shuruat) kerengey jis ka zikr Allah Taala ney pehley farmaya hai. phir aap ney ye aayat tilawat farmaee : (اِنَّ الصَّفَا وَ الْمَرْوَۃَ مِنْ شَعَآئِرِ اللّٰہِ),""bilashuba Safa aur Marwa Allah Taala ki muqarrar karda alaamaat mein sey hain.''"
2974,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kohe-Safa par chadhey yahan tak ke jab aap ki nazar Baitullah par padi to aap ney Allahu-Akbar kaha.
2975,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab kohe-Safa par thehertey to teen dafa Allahu-Akbar kehtey, phir ye padhtey : (لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللّٰہُ وَحْدَہُ …),''Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin. wo yaktaa hai. us ka koi shareek nahin. badshahi aur tareef usi ki hai aur wo har chiz par khub qadir hai.''ye teen dafa padhtey aur dua kartey, phir Marwa par bhi aisey hi kartey."
2976,Hazrat Muhammad Baaqar (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Haj key barey mein suna ke aap kohe-Safa par khadey ho kar (bar-bar) (لا الہ الا اللہ) padhtey they aur us zikr key doran mein duayen bhi farmatey they.
2977,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Baitullah key saat chakkar lagaey. un mein sey teen chakkaron mein kandhey hilla kar tez tez chaley aur chaar chakkar aaram sey chaley, phir maqame-Ibrahim key paas aa khadey huye aur do rakaten padhin aur ye aayat padhi : (وَ اتَّخِذُوْا مِنْ مَّقَامِ اِبْرٰھٖیمَ مُصَلًّی)''tum maqame-Ibrahim ko namaz ki jagah banao.'' ye aayat aap ney logon ko sunaney key liye buland aawaz sey padhi. phir dobara Hajare-Aswad key paas gaey aur usey bosa diya, phir (bahir ko) chaley aur farmaya : hum us (pahadi) sey ibtida (shuruat) kerengey jiska zikr Allah Taala ney pehley farmaya hai. iskey baad aap pehley Safa par gaey. is par chadhey yahan tak ke aap ko Baitullah nazar aaney laga. aap ney teen dafa farmaya : (لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا Allah … )'''Allah key siwa koi (sachcha) mabood nahin. wo yaktaa hai. us ka koi shareek nahin. badshahat usi ki hai. tamam taareefon usi key liye hain. wohi zinda karta aur maut deta hai aur wo har chiz par qadir hai.'' phir aap (Allahu-Akbar) aur (Alhamdulillah) padhtey rahey, phir aap ney duayen farmaeen jo aap key muqaddar mein thin, phir nichey utarney lagey yahan tak ke jab aap key qadame-mubarak nasheb (dhalaan) mein ja pahunchey to aap daudney lagey, yahan tak ke aap key qadam (Marwa ki chadhai) chadhney lagey to aap ney phir chalna shuru kar diya yahan tak ke Marwa tak pahunch gaey, phir aap is par chadhey yahan tak ke aap ko Baitullah nazar aaney laga to aap ney teen dafa ye padha : ( لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا Allah … ),''Allah key siwa koi (sachcha) mabood nahin. wo akela hai. us ka koi shareek nahin. badshahi aur tareef usi ko zebaa hai aur wo har chiz par khub qudrat rakhney wala hai.''phir aap Allah Taala ka zikr farmatey rahey aur tasbih aur tahmeed kartey rahey, phir jo Allah Taala ney chaha, duayen farmaeen. sab chakkaron mein isi tarah kartey rahey yahan tak ke (Safa, Marwa key) tawaf sey farigh ho gaey."
2978,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hajjatul-wadaa mein Baitullah aur Safa, Marwa key tawaf apni oontni par kiye taake log aap ko dekh saken aur aap un sey unchey hon aur wo aap sey sawal kar saken kyonkey logon ney aap ko gher rakha tha."
2979,Hazrat Kasir bin Jumhaan bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan chaltey dekha. (mainey un sey puchha) to unhoney farmaya : agar main chalta hun to mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko chaltey dekha hai aur agar main daudta to mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko daudtey bhi dekha hai.
2980,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, phir unhoney mandarja baala (upar bayan hui) riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya magar (aakhir mein) kaha ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main boodha aadmi hun."
2981,Imam Zohri bayan kartey hain ke logon ney Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan ramal kartey dekha hai? to unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon ki eik jamaat mein they aur wo log ramal kar rahey they. mera khayal hai wo aap key ramal karney ki wajeh hi sey ramal kar rahey they.
2982,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan is liye daudey they ke mushrekin ko apni quwat dikhayen.
2983,eik Sahaabiya (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko wadi key pet mein daudtey dekha hai. aap farma rahey they : is wadi ko zarur daud kartey kiya jaey.
2984,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Safa sey utartey they to aaram sey chaltey they yahan tak ke jab aap key qadam wadi key pet mein nashebi (dhalaan ki) jagah pahunchtey to aap daudney lagtey yahan tak ke wadi sey nikal jatey.
2985,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key qadam mubarak wadi key pet mein nashebi (dhalaan ki) jagah mein utartey to kandhey hila kar tez tez chaltey yahan tak ke wadi sey nikal jatey.
2986,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kohe-Safa sey utrey yahan tak ke jab aap key qadam mubarak wadi mein utrey to aap ney ramal kiya, yahan tak ke jab chadhna shuru huye to phir chalney lagey."
2987,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Marwa key paas aaye aur is par chadhey yahan tak ke aap ko Baitullah nazar aaney laga to aap ney teen dafa ye dua padhi : (لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللّٰہُ وَحْدَہُ …), ''Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, wo akela hai, us ka koi shareek nahin, badshahi aur tareef usi ko zebaa hai. aur wo har chiz par khub qadir hai.''phir aap ney Allah Taala ka zikr farmaya, tasbih aur tahmeed ki aur phir jo Allah ney chaha aap ney dua ki. (phir har dafa isi tarah kartey rahey) yahan tak ke (Safa aur Marwa key) tawaf (saee) sey farigh ho gaey."
2988,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kohe-Safa ki taraf gaey. is par chadhey yahan tak ke aap ko Baitullah nazar aaney laga, phir aap ney Allah Taala ki tohid aur takbir bayan ki aur kaha : (لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللّٰہُ وَحْدَہُ لَا شَرِیْکَ … ),''Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, wo akela hai, us ka koi shareek nahin, usi key liye badshahi aur tareef hai. wo zindagi aur maut deta hai. aur har chiz par khub qudrat rakhta hai.''phir aap wapis chaley yahan tak ke jab aap key qadam nasheb (dhaali) mein pahunchey to aap daudney lagey, yahan tak ke jab aap key qadam chadhai chadhney lagey, aap aahista chalney lagey yahan tak ke Marwa par pahunchey, phir is par bhi aap ney isi tarah kiya jis tarah Safa par kiya tha (phir isi tarah kartey rahey) yahan tak ke aap ney apney chakkar purey kar liye."
2989,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sathiyon ney Safa aur Marwa ka sirf eik dafa tawaf kiya.
2990,Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key umerey mein aap key baal mubarak Marwa par eik teer key sath kaatey they.
2991,Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key baal Marwa par eik erabi (dehati) key teer sey kaatey they.
2992,Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Baitullah aur Safa aur Marwa key tawaf sey farigh huye to mainey aap key baalon key kinarey apney eik teer sey kaatey they. aur ye zul-hijja key pehley dahey ki baat hai. raawi Qais ney kaha : ulama Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key in alfaz ko durust nahin samajhtey.
2993,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hum (Hajjatul-wadaa mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath (Makka Mukarrama ko) nikley. hum (mein sey aksar) sirf Haj ki niyat rakhtey they. jab aap ney Baitullah aur Safa, Marwa key tawaf kar liye to aap ney farmaya : jis shakhs key sath qurbani ka janwer hai, wo apney ehraam par qaaim rahey aur jis shakhs key sath qurbani ka janwer nahin, wo halal ho jaey."
2994,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Hajjatul-wadaa mein nikley. hum mein sey kuchh ney Haj ka ehraam baandha aur baaz ney umrey ka. baaz qurbani ka janwer bhi sath laye they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney Umerey ka ehraam baandha aur wo qurbani nahin laya to (umrah karney key baad) wo halal ho jaey. aur jisney umerey ka ehraam baandha aur wo qurbani bhi sath laya hai to wo (qurbani zibeh honey sey pehley) halal na ho. aur jis shakhs ney Haj ka ehraam baandha hai wo apna Haj mukammal kerey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mainey umrey ka ehraam baandha tha.
2995,"Hazrat Asma binte Abi Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) farmati hain ke hum (Hajjatul-wadaa mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Haj ki labbaik kehtey huye (Makka ko) aaye. jab hum Makka Mukarrama key qarib huye to aap ney farmaya : jis shakhs key sath qurbani ka janwer nahin, wo (umrah kar key) halal ho jaey aur jis shakhs key sath qurbani ka janwer hai wo apney ehraam par qaaim rahey. Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : (merey khawind) Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) key sath qurbani ka janwer tha, lihaza wo apney ehraam par qaaim rahey. merey sath qurbani ka janwer nahin tha, is liye mein halal ho gaee. aur mainey apney aam kapdey pehan liye aur khushbu bhi lagai, phir main Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) key qarib ho kar bethi to wo kehney lagey : mujh sey door ho kar betho. mainey (mazaq mein) kaha : kya aap ko khatra hai ke main aap par zabardasti kood padoongi?"
2996,"Baraa't wali aayaat aakhir tak padhin phir qurbaaniyon wala din ( das zul-hijja ) huwa to hamney tawaf ifaaza kya. jab Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ( tawaf sey) wapis lotey to logon sey khitab farmaya aur unhein muzdalfa sey lotney , qurbaaniyaan karney aur dusri عبادات Haj key tareeqey bayan kiye. jab wo farigh huye to Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huye aur logon key samney bara-at wali aayaat aakhir tak padhein jab Mina sey wapsi ka pehla din huwa to Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huye, logon sey khitab farmaya aur unhein bataya ke wo kaisey wapis jaeyngey aur kaisey ramii kerengey. isi tarah unhein manaasik Haj ki taalim di. jab wo farigh huye to Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) uthey aur logon key samney bara-at wali aayaat aakhir tak padhi.Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai) bayan kartey hain : Abdullah bin Usman bin Khaseem ilme-hadees mein qawi nahin. mainey un ki hadees sirf is liye bayan ki hai ke kahin ibne Juraij an Abi Zubair ki sanad ko sahih na samajh liya jaaey. mainey ye hadees (ibne Khaseem key wastey wali ) sirf Is-haq bin Raahwiya bin Ibrahim sey likhi hai. wesey Yahya bin Saeed Qataan aur Abdur-Rehman bin Mahdi ney ibn Khaseem ki hadees ko sirey sey tark kiya hua qarar nahin diya, albatta Ali bin Madini ney farmaya hai ke ibne Khaseem ki hadees munkir (zaeef) hoti hai. aur Imam Ali bin Madini ka martaba ye hai ke goya wo sirf ilme hadees hi key liye paida huye hain."
2997,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath zul-hijja ki chaar taareekh ko (Makka Mukarrama) pahunchey to Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : halal ho jao, aur Haj key ehraam ko umrey mein badal lo. hum is sey bahut tang dil huye aur ye baat hum par bahut shaaq guzri. ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pahunchi to aap ney farmaya : aey logo ! halal ho jao, agar merey sath qurbani ka janwer na hota to main bhi isi tarah karta jis tarah tum karogey. hum halal ho gaey yahan tak ke hamney aurton sey jima (sambhog) kiya aur hamney wo sab kaam kiye jo eik halal shakhs karta hai, yahan tak ke jab tarwiya ka din huwa aur hum Makkey sey bahar nikley to hamney Haj ki labbaik pukaari."
2998,"Hazrat Imran Ansari sey riwayat hai ke main Makka Mukarrama key raastey main eik darkht key nichey utra huwa tha ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) raastey sey hat kar merey paas aaye aur farmaney lagey : is darkht key nichey kyon utrey ho? mainey kaha : saye ki khatir. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to Mina key do pahadon key darmiyan ho, aur aap ney apna haath mashriq ki taraf badhaya, to wahan eik wadi hai jisey sarba … ya Haris (bin Miskeen) ki hadees key mutabiq, sarar… kaha jata hai, us wadi main eik darkht hai jis key nichey sattar Nabi paida huye."
2999,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Mina mein khitab farmaya : Allah Taala ney hamarey kaan khol diye yahan tak ke hum aap ka har farman ba-khoobi sun rahey they, halanke hum apney apney khemon mein they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon ko manaasike-hajj (hajj ke arkaan) ki taalim dey rahey they yahan tak ke rami wali kankariyon ki baat aai to aap ney farmaya ke wo hazaf ki kankariyon jaisi chhoti hain. aap ney muhajrin ko hukm diya ke wo masjide (khaif) ki agli janib utren aur ansaar ko hukm diya ke wo masjid ki pichli janib utren."
3000,Hazrat abdul-Azeez bin Rafeea' bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha ke mujhey koi aisi chiz bataiye jo aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey samjhi ho. mujhey bataeyn ke aap ney tarwiya key din Zohar ki namaz kahan padhi thi? unhoney farmaya : Mina mein. mainey kaha : wapsi (13-zul-hijja) key din Asr ki namaz kahan padhi? farmaya : Abtah mein.
3001,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Mina sey Arafat gaey. koi labbaik kehta tha aur koi takbeeren.
3002,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Arafat gaey. hum mein sey koi labbaik kehta tha aur koi takbeeren kehta tha.
3003,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Abu-Bakar Saqafi sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha jabkey hum Mina sey Arafat ja rahey they : tum us din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath kis tarah labbaik kehtey they? to unhoney kaha : labbaik kehney wala labbaik kehta tha, is par koi aetraz nahin kiya jata tha. aur takbeeren kehney wala takbeeren kehta tha, is par koi aetraz nahin kiya jata tha."
3004,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Abu-Bakar Saqafi bayan kartey hain ke mainey Arfey key din ki subah Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha is din labbaik kehney key barey mein aap kya kehtey hain? wo farmaney lagey : main us din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sahaba key sath chala. un mein sey koi takbeeren kehta tha aur koi labbaik padhta tha, lekin koi eik dusrey par aetraz nahin karta tha."
3005,"Hazrat Taariq bin Shahaab sey riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi ney Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : agar ye aayat : (اَلْیَوْمَ اَکْمَلْتُ لَکُمْ دِیْنَکُمْ),hum yahudiyon par utarti to hum us din ko eid bana letey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mujhey us din ka ba-khoobi ilm hai jis din ye aayat utri balke us raat ka bhi jis raat ye utri. wo Jumey ki raat thi aur hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Arafat mein they."
3006,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : youme-Arfa sey badh kar koi din aisa nahin jis mein Allah Taala ziyada ghulam londiyan aag sey azad karta ho. us din Allah Taala mazeed qarib aa jata hai, phir apney un bandon (hujjaaj kiram) ki bina par farishton key samney fakhr karta hai aur farmata hai : merey ye bandey kya chahtey hain? Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke bahut mumkin hai ke (sanad mein ibne Musayib key shagrid) Yunus sey murad Yunus bin Yusuf ho, jin sey Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi Alaih) riwayat kartey hain. (Allah ziyzda behtar jaanta hai)."
3007,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : youme-Arfa (9-zul-hijja) youme-nahar (qurbani ka din) (10-zul-hijja) aur ayyaame-tashreeq (11,12,13- zul-hijja) hum musalmanon key liye eid key din hain aur ye khaney peeney key din hain."
3008,"Hazrat Salim bin Abdullah sey riwayat hai ke khalifa Abdul-Malik bin Marwan ney (Ameere-hajj) Hujjaaj bin Yusuf ko likha aur hukm diya ke Haj key masaayel mein Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki mukhalifat na kerey. jab Arfey ka din huwa to suraj dhalney key waqt Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Hujjaaj ki taraf aaye. main bhi aap key sath tha. aap ney uskey khemey key paas aa kar buland aawaz sey kaha : kidhar hai woh? Hujjaaj bahar nikla. us ney eik zard rang mein rangi hui chadar odhi hui thi. kehney laga : aey Abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kya baat hai? aap ney farmaya : agar to sunnat par amal karna chahta hai to (khutbey aur namaz key liye) chal. us ney kaha : is waqt? aap ney farmaya : haan ! us ney kaha : main zara jism par pani dal lun, phir main aap key paas aata hun. aap us ka intizar karney lagey yahan tak ke wo nikla aur merey aur merey walid (Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) key darmiyan chalney laga. mainey kaha : agar tum sunnat par amal karna chahtey ho to khutba mukhtasar karna aur wuqoof jaldi shuru kar dena. wo Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf dekhney laga taake un sey bhi is ki tasdeeq sun ley. jab Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye dekha to farmaya : is ney durust kaha hai."
3009,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) key sath Arafat mein tha. wo farmaney lagey : kya wajeh hai ke main logon ko labbaik pukartey nahin sunta? mainey kaha : wo Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey dartey hain. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) apney khemey sey nikley aur buland aawaz sey pukara : (لَبَّیْکَ اللّٰھُمَّ لَبَّیْکَ لَبَّیْکَ),tajjub hai ke unhoney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey bughz rakhney ki wajeh sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat chhod di hai."
3010,Hazrat Nabeet (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Arafat mein namaz sey pehley eik surkh oont par khutba irshad farmatey dekha.
3011,Hazrat Nabeet (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Arfey key din surkh oont par khutba irshad farmatey dekha.
3012,"Hazrat Salim bin Abdullah sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) Arfey key din, junhi suraj dhalaa, Hujjaaj bin Yusuf key paas aaye. main bhi unkey sath tha. wo farmaney lagey : agar to sunnat par amal karna chahta hai to Abhi (khutbey aur namaz key liye) chal. wo kehney laga : is waqt? unhoney farmaya : haan. Hazrat Salim ney kaha : mainey Hujjaaj sey kaha : agar to aaj sunnat par amal karna chahta hai to khutba mukhtasar karna aur namaz jald shuru karna. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney (bator tasdeeq) farmaya : is ney durust kaha."
3013,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har namaz uskey waqt par padhtey they magar Muzdalfa aur Arafat mein (jama kartey they).
3014,Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main (dorane-wuqoof) arafat mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechey sawar tha. aap haath utha kar dua karney lagey. itney mein aap ki oontni eik taraf ko mudi to mahaar (nakel) aap key haath sey gir padi. aap ney eik haath sey mahaar pakad li aur doosra haath (dua key liye) uthaey rakha.
3015,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : Quraish Muzdalfa mein thehar jatey they. wo apney aap ko hims kehtey they. aur baqi Arab Arafat mein wuqoof kartey they. Allah Taala ney apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko hukm diya ke aap Arfey mein thehren, phir wahan sey wapis loten. tab Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaari : (ثُمَّ اَفِیْضُوْا مِنْ حَیْثُ اَفَاضَ النَّاسُ),''tum bhi wahan sey lota karo jahan sey dusrey log laut'tey hain.''"
3016,Hazrat Juber bin Mut'im (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mera eik oont gum ho gaya. main usey talash karney key liye arfa pahunch gaya. ye Arfey ka din tha. mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko wahan wuqoof kartey dekha. mainey (dil mein) kaha : aap ka yahan kya kaam? aap to hims mein sey hain.
3017,Hazrat Yazid bin Shebaan bayan kartey hain ke hum Arafat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki jaey wuqoof sey bahut door thehrey huye they. hamarey paas Hazrat ibne Murabba' Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur farmaya : main tumhari taraf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka qaasid hun. aap farma rahey hain ke apni apni jagahon par thehrey raho. tum apney buzurg Hazrat Ibrahim alehissalam ki virasat par qaaim ho.
3018,Hazrat Muhammad Baaqar (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke hum Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaey aur un sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Haj key barey mein puchha to unhoney bayan kiya ke Allah Taala key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Arafat sarey ka sara wuqoof ki jagah hai.
3019,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yaamar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir tha ke aap key paas kuchh log aaye aur aap sey Haj key barey mein sawalaat kiye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Haj wuqoofey-Arfa (Arfaa mein theherney) ka naam hai. jo shakhs Muzdalfa mein guzari janey wali raat ki subah tulu honey sey pehley Arafat (sey ho kar muzdalfa) aa jaey us ka Haj pura ho gaya.
3020,Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Arafat sey wapis lotey to Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) aap key peechhey sawari par bethey they. aap dono haath uthaey dua farma rahey they ke aap ki oontni bidak gaee. aap key haath mubarak aap key sar sey unchey nahin hotey they. aap isi haalat mein chaltey rahey yahan tak ke Muzdalfa pahunch gaey.
3021,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Arfey sey wapis lotey to main aap key peechhey sawari par betha tha. aap ney apni sawari ki mahaar (nakel) khinch rakhi thi yahan tak ke uskey kaan ki (jad aur) haddi paalaan ki agli lakdi ko lag rahi thi. aap farma rahey they : aey logo ! itminan aur waqar ikhtiyar karo, oonton ko tez bhagaaney sey neki hasil nahin hoti."
3022,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) arafat sey wapis lot rahey they to aap ney apni oontni ki mahaar (nakel) khinch rakhi thi, yahan tak ke us ka sar paalaan ki darmiyani lakdi ko lagta tha. aap logon sey farma rahey they : sukoon ikhtiyar karo sukoon. ye Arfey key din Sham ki baat hai."
3023,"Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey, jo ke aap key peechhey sawari par bethey they, riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab (Arfa sey Muzdalfa ki taraf ) lotey to Arfey ki sham aur Muzdalfa ki subah logon ko farmatey rahey : sukoon aur waqar ikhtiyar karo. khud aap ney apni oontni ki mahaar (nakel) khinch rakhi thi yahan tak ke jab aap wadi mohsir mein dakhil huye jo ke Mina ka hissa hai to aap ney farmaya : rami key liye khazaf ki kankariyon jaisi (chhoti-chhoti) kankariyaan uthana. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) musalsal labbaik kehtey rahey yahan tak ke aap ney Jamara, Aqba ko rami karna shuru kar diya."
3024,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wapsi ka safar kiya to itminan aur sukoon sey chaltey rahey aur logon ko sukoon aur itminan sey chalney ka hukm diya, albatta wadi mohsir mein apni sawari ko tez kar liya aur logon ko hukm diya ke wo Jamraa Aqba (aur dusrey jamaraat) ko khazaf ki kankariyon jaisi kankariyon sey rami karen."
3025,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Arafat sey wapis chaley to farmatey they : aey Allah key bando ! sukoon aur itminan ikhtiyar karo. aap apney haath sey is tarah ishara farma rahey they. aur (raawi hadees) Ayub ney apni hatheli sey aasman ki taraf ishara kiya.
3026,Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey Hajjatul-wadaa mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (ki sawari) ki chaal key barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney farmaya : darmiyani chaal chaltey they. jab khaali jagah paatey to sawari ko mazeed tez farma detey.
3027,Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Arafat sey wapis lotey to (raastey mein) eik ghaati ki taraf ho liye. mainey arz kiya : (Allah key Rasool !) Maghrib ki namaz padhengey? farmaya : (nahin) namaz ki jagah to aagey (muzdalfa mein) hai.
3028,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (Arafat sey wapsi key doran mein) us ghaati mein utrey they jahan (aaj kal) Ameer aur Hukkaam utartey hain. aap ney peshab kiya, phir halka sa wuzu kiya. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! namaz padhengey? farmaya : (nahin) namaz to aagey (Muzdalfa mein) ja kar padhengey. jab hum Muzdalfa mein aaye to abhi sab logon ney oonton sey saman nahin utarey they ke aap ney Maghrib ki namaz padhaai."
3029,Hazrat Abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Maghrib aur Isha ko Muzdalfa mein jama kar key padha tha.
3030,Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Maghrib aur Isha ki namazen Muzdalfa mein jama kar key padhi thin.
3031,Hazrat Salim key walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Maghrib aur Isha ki namazein Muzdalfa main eik iqaamat key sath padhi thin. inkey darmiyan ya inkey baad aap ney koi nawaafil ada nahin kiye.
3032,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Maghrib aur Isha ki namazon ko jama kiya. unkey darmiyan koi nawaafil nahin padhey. Maghrib ki teen rakaat padhin aur Isha ki do. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi isi tarah jama kartey they yahan tak ke Allah sey ja miley.
3033,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Maghrib aur Isha ko Muzdalfa main eik iqaamat key sath jama kiya.
3034,"Hazrat Kureb sey manqul hai ke mainey Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha kyonkey wo Arfey ki sham (wapsi key waqt) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey sawari par bethey they, mainey kaha : tum ney kaisey kiya? unhoney farmaya : hum chaltey aaye yahan tak ke Muzdalfa pahunch gaey. aap utrey aur Maghrib ki namaz padhi, phir aap ney logon ko pegham bheja to unhoney apney oonton ko apni qiyam gaahon mein bithaya, lekin unhoney saman nahin utara yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Isha ki namaz padhaai, phir logon ney apna saman waghera utara aur apni qiyam gaahon mein thehrey. jab subah hui to main Quraish key jald janey walon mein pedal chal pada. aur Hazrat Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) aap key peechhey sawari par beth gaey."
3035,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main un logon mein shamil tha jinhein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Muzdalfa ki raat apney kamzoron (yani aurton, bachchon, boodhon, mareezon waghera) key sath pehley bheja tha."
3036,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main un logon mein shamil tha, jinhein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Muzdalfa ki raat apney kamzoron, yani aurton aur bachchon mein pehley hi bhej diya tha."
3037,Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney bani Haashim key kamzoron (aurton aur bachchon) ko hukm diya tha ke wo Muzdalfa sey raat hi ko chal paden.
3038,Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ney bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey hukm diya tha ke main raat key andherey mein Muzdalfa sey Mina ko chali jaun.
3039,Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein raat key andherey mein Muzdalfa sey Mina ko chaley jaya kartey they.
3040,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ko Muzdalfa sey Fajr tulu honey sey qabl chal padney ki ijazat Is liye di thi ke wo bhari jism wali sust raftaar aurat thin.
3041,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey kabhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko be-waqt namaz padhtey nahin dekha magar Maghrib aur Isha ki namazen jo aap ney Muzdalfa mein (bahut raat gaey) padhin aur usi raat Fajr ki namaz bhi aap ney waqt (moataad) sey pehley padhi.
3042,"Hazrat Urwa bin Muzris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Muzdalfa mein wuqoof farmatey (thehrey) dekha. aap ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney ye namaz (Namaze Fajr) is jagah hamarey sath padhi, phir hamarey sath thehra raha aur wo is sey qabl din ya raat kisi waqt Arafat mein wuqoof kar chuka ho to us ka Haj pura ho gaya."
3043,"Hazrat Urwa bin Muzris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney Imam aur logon key sath Muzdalfa ka wuqoof pa liya aur phir wo Mina ko gaya to usney Haj pa liya (ba-sharte-ke wo is sey pehley Arafat sey ho aaya ho). aur jis shakhs ney logon aur Imam key sath ye wuqoof na paya (yani itna let ho gaya) to us ka Haj nahin huwa."
3044,Hazrat Urwa bin Muzris (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas Muzdalfa aaya. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main banu Tey key do pahadon sey aaya hun. mainey kisi tiley ya pahad ko nahin chhoda magar is par wuqoof kiya hai to kya mera Haj ho gaya? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney ye namaz (Fajr ki) hamarey sath padhi jabkey wo is sey pehley raat ya din key kisi hissey mein Arafat mein wuqoof kar chuka ho to us ka Haj pura ho gaya aur us ney apna mail kuchail door kar liya.
3045,Hazrat Urwa bin Muzris bin Aus bin Harisa bin Lam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas Muzdalfa mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : kya mera Haj ho gaya hai? aap ney farmaya : jisney ye namaz (Namaze-Fajr) hamarey sath (Muzdalfa mein) padhi aur hamarey sath ye wuqoof (wuqoofe-Muzdalfa) kiya yahan tak ke Mina ko jaaey aur is sey pehley wo raat ya din ko kisi waqt Arafat sey ho aaya ho to us ka Haj pura ho gaya aur us ney apna mail kuchail door kar liya.
3046,"Hazrat Urwa bin Muzris Taai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur arz kiya ke main aap key paas banu Tey key pahadon sey aaya hun. mainey apni sawari ko thakaa diya hai aur apney aap ko bhi mashaqqat mein dala hai. jo bhi teela ya pahad aaya, mainey is par wuqoof kiya hai, to kya mera Haj ho gaya? aap ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney subah ki namaz yahan (Muzdalfa mein) hamarey sath padh li jabkey wo is sey pehley Arafat sey ho aaya ho to us ney apna mail kuchail door kar liya aur us ka Haj pura ho gaya."
3047,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yaamer Daili (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas Arfey mein mojud tha jabkey aap key paas Najad walon mein sey kuchh log aaye. unhoney eik aadmi sey kaha to usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey Haj key barey mein sawal kiya. aap ney farmaya : Haj wuqoofe-Arfa ka naam hai. jo shakhs (Arfa sey ho kar) subah ki namaz sey pehley Muzdalfa mein aa gaya, us ney Haj pa liya. Mina key din teen hain : jo shakhs do din thehar kar jaldi aa jaey to is par koi gunah nahin aur jo shakhs teesrey din bhi thehra raha, is par bhi koi gunah nahin. phir aap ney apney peechhey eik aadmi bithaya jo logon mein ye aelan karta tha."
3048,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Muzdalfa sarey ka sara wuqoof ki jagah hai.
3049,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yazid sey riwayat hai ke hum Muzdalfa mein they ke Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey us shakhsiyat ko jis par Sura Baqra utaari gaee, is jagah (لَبَّیْکَ اللّٰھُمَّ لَبَّیْکَ) pukartey suna."
3050,"Hazrat Amr bin Memnon bayan kartey hain ke mainey dekha ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Muzdalfa mein farma rahey they : jahiliyat waley suraj tulu honey sey pehley Muzdalfa sey nahin chaltey they balke kehtey they : aey sabeer ! roshan ho. lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un ki mukhalifat farmaee, phir wo tulu shams sey pehley hi chal padey."
3051,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey kamzor, aurton aur bachchon mein (raat hi ko) bhej diya tha. hamney subah ki namaz Mina mein padhi aur Jamara (Aqba) ko kankariyaan maarin."
3052,"Ummul-Mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke kaash! main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey (Muzdalfa sey raat ko Mina chaley janey ki) ijazat talab karti, jaisey Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ney ijazat talab kar li thi aur main bhi Fajr ki namaz logon key aaney sey pehley Mina mein padh leti. Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) bojhal aur sust raftaar khatoon thin. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ijazat talab kar li thi aur aap ney unhein ijazat dey di thi. to unhoney Fajr ki namaz Mina mein padhi aur logon key aaney sey pehley rami kar li thi."
3053,Hazrat Asma binte Abi Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key eik Mola (azad karda ghulam) sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat Asma binte Abi Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key sath raat key andherey hi mein Mina aa gaya to mainey un sey kaha ke hum Mina mein andherey hi mein aagey hain. wo farmaney lagin : hum us shakhsiyat key hotey huye aisa kya kartey they jo tujh (aur hum) sey bahut afzal thi.
3054,"Hazrat Urwa bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha gaya, jabkey main bhi unkey paas betha tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Hajjatul-wadaa mein wapis chaley to aap ki raftaar kaisi thi? unhoney farmaya : aap apni oontni ko darmiyani chaal sey chala rahey they, albatta jab khaali jagah paatey to (mazeed) tez farma detey."
3055,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wadi mohsir mein oontni ko bahut tez kar diya tha.
3056,"Hazrat Muhammad Baaqar (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey marwi hai ke hum Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaey aur mainey un sey kaha : hamein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Haj key barey mein bayan farmaiye. unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Muzdalfa sey suraj tulu honey sey pehley chal padey aur aap ney Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko apney peechhey sawari par bitha liya yahan tak ke jab wadi mohsir mein pahunchey to sawari ko kuchh tez kar diya, phir us darmiyani raastey sey chaley jo tujhey badey Jamre (Jamara Aqba) par ja pahunchaata hai, yahan tak ke aap us Jamre key paas pahunchey jo shajra key paas hai, phir aap ney saat kankariyaan maarin. har kankarii key sath (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey they. aur wo kankariyaan khazaf ki kankariyon jaisi (chhoti chhoti) thin. aap ney ye rami wadi key nasheb (dhaal) ki taraf sey ki thi."
3057,Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey sawar tha (yani Muzdalfa sey Mina tak). aap labbaik kehtey rahey yahan tak ke aap ney Jamre ki rami shuru ki.
3058,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) labbaik padhtey rahey yahan tak ke aap ney Jamre ko rami ki.
3059,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Jamra Aqba ki rami wali subah (10 zul-hijja) ko, jabkey aap apni sawari par sawar they, farmaya : merey liye kankariyaan chuno. mainey (chhoti chhoti) kankariyaan chunin jo khazaf ki kankariyon jaisi thin. jab mainey wo aap key haath mein rakhin to aap ney farmaya : is qisam ki kankariyon sey rami kerni chahiye. Deen mein ghulu (had sey badh janey) sey bacho kyonkey tum sey pehli qomon ko Deen mein ghulu ney halak kiya."
3060,Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney logon ko Arafat sey sham ko chaltey waqt aur Muzdalfa ki subah farmaya : sukoon aur itminan ikhtiyar karo. khud aap ney apni oontni ki mahaar (nakel) khinch rakhi thi yahan tak ke jab aap Mina mein dakhil huye aur wadi mohsir mein utrey to aap ney farmaya : khazaf ki kankariyon jaisi kankariyaan chun'na jin sey Jamaraat ko rami ki jaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney haath sey ishara bhi farma rahey they jis tarah koi shakhs kankari phainktaa hai.
3061,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Jamra Aqba ki rami wali subah (10 zul-hijja ko) farmaya, jabkey aap apni oontni par sawar they : merey liye kankariyaan chun kar la. mainey (chhoti chhoti) kankariyaan chunin jo khazaf wali kankariyon ki tarah thin. aap ney unhein apney haath mein pakda. aap unhein apney daste-mubarak mein hila rahey they aur farma rahey they : in jaisi kankariyon sey rami kerni chahiye."
3062,"Hazrat Ummey Husain (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Haj waley saal Haj kiya. mainey dekha ke Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki sawari ki mahaar (nakel) pakad kar aagey aagey chal rahey hain aur Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap par kapda taanaa huwa hai taake dhoop sey saya ho sakey. us waqt aap ehraam sey they yahan tak ke aap ney Jamra Aqba ko rami ki, phir aap ney logon sey khitab farmaya. Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa ki aur bahut si baaten irshad farmaeen."
3063,"Hazrat Qudaama bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko qurbaaniyon waley din apni bhurey rang ki oontni par sawar Jamara Aqba ko rami kartey dekha. na sawaariyon ko maara ja raha tha, na unhein bhagaayaa ja raha tha aur na hato bacho ka shor tha."
3064,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko oont par sawar Jamara ko rami kartey dekha. aap farma rahey they : aey logo ! mujh sey Haj ki ibadaton key tareeqey seekh lo. shayad main is saal key baad Haj na kar sakun.
3065,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qurbani waley din chaasht key waqt (din chadhey) rami ki aur youm nahar (qurbaniwaley din) key baad jab suraj dhalta, us waqt ramii kartey."
3066,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamein, yani khandan Abdul-Muttalib key bachchon ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney gadhon par sawar kar key (subah sey pehley hi) bhej diya tha. aap hamari raanon ko thap-thapaatey they aur farmatey they : aey merey beto ! suraj tulu honey sey pehley Jamraa Aqba ko rami na karna."
3067,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney ghar walon (aurton aur bachchon) ko subah sey pehley hi bhej diya tha. aur aap ney unhein hukm diya tha ke jab tak suraj tulu na ho, wo Jamre ko rami na karen."
3068,Ummul-Mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni eik zauja mohtarma (biwi) ko ijazat di thi ke wo Muzdalfa sey raat hi ko chali jaey aur ja kar Jamra Aqba ko rami karey aur subah key waqt apney (Mina waley) khemey mein pahunch jaey. hadees ke raawi Hazrat Ata bhi apni wafat tak isi tarah kartey rahey.
3069,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey Mina key dino mein mukhtalif sawalaat kiye jatey they to aap farmatey they : koi harj nahin. chunanche eik aadmi ney puchha : mainey qurbani zibeh karney sey qabl sar mundaa liya hai. aap ney farmaya : koi harj nahin. eik aadmi ney kaha : mainey Sham honey key baad rami ki hai. aap ney farmaya : koi harj nahin.
3070,Hazrat Adi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney charwaahon ko rukhsat di hai ke wo eik din rami kar lein aur eik din chhod lein.
3071,"Hazrat Aasim bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney charwaahon ko (Mina sey) bahar raat guzarney ki ijazat di hai, isi ke sath wo youme-nahar (qurbani wale din) ko rami karen aur baad waley do dino ki rami un mein sey kisi eik din ikhatti ada kar len."
3072,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yazid sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha gaya : kuchh log Jamre ko ghaati key ooper sey rami kartey hain. Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney wadi key nasheb (dhalaan) sey rami ki aur farmaya : qism uski jis key siwa koi mabood nahin ! is jagah sey rami ki thi us shakhsiyat ney jin par Sura Baqra utaari gaee.
3073,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yazid sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney Jamre ko saat kankariyaan maarin. Baitullah ko apni baain janib aur Arfey ko apni daeyn janib kiya aur farmaya : ye hai us shakhsiyat ki rami ki jagah jin par Sura Baqra utaari qaee. Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke main nahin janta ke ibne-Abi Adi key ilawa kisi raawi ney is hadees mein Mansoor ka zikr kiya ho. (Allah behtar janta hai).
3074,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yazid bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, unhoney wadi key pet sey Jamra Aqba ko rami ki, phir farmaya : qism us zaat ki jis key siwa koi mabood nahin ! ye us shakhsiyat key rami karney ki jagah hai jin par Sura Baqra utaari gaee."
3075,"Hazrat Aa'mash sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hujjaaj ko ye kehtey suna ke Sura Baqra na kaho balke yun kaho : wo sura jis mein gaaey ka zikr kiya gaya hai. mainey ye baat Hazrat Ibrahim Nakhai sey zikr ki. wo farmaney lagey : mujhey Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yazid ney bayan kiya ke main Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key sath tha jab unhoney Jamara Aqba ko rami ki. aap wadi key pet mein khadey huye aur Jamre ki taraf munh kiya, phir usey saat kankariyaan maarin. har kankari key sath Allahu-Akbar kaha. mainey kaha : kuchh log pahad par chadh kar rami kartey hain. farmaney lagey : qism us zaat ki jis key siwa koi mabood nahin ! is jagah mainey us shakhsiyat ko rami kartey dekha jin par Sura Baqra utaari gaee."
3076,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Jamre ko khazaf ki kankariyon jaisi (chhoti-chhoti) kankariyaan maarin.
3077,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap Jamaron ko khazaf ki (chhoti-chhoti) kankariyon jaisi kankariyon key sath rami kartey they.
3078,"Hazrat Muhammad Baaqar (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke hum Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaey. mainey arz kiya : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Haj key barey mein bataiye. unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us Jamre ko jo darkht key paas hai, saat kankariyaan maarin. aap har kankari key sath Allahu-Akbar kehtey they. kankariyaan khazaf ki kankariyon jaisi thin aur aap ney ye rami wadi key pet sey ki thi, phir aap qurban gaah ki taraf gaey aur qurbani ki."
3079,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke hum Hajjatul-wadaa mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath lotey to hum mein sey kuchh log keh rahey they : hamney saat kankariyaan maari hain aur baaz keh rahey they : hamney chhe kankariyaan maari hain, taaham kisi ney eik dusrey par aeb nahin lagaya."
3080,Hazrat Abu-Mujliz bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey Jamaron key barey mein puchha to wo farmaney lagey : main nahin janta ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein saat-saat kankariyaan maarin ya chhe-chhe.
3081,Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey sawari par betha huwa tha. aap labbaik kehtey rahey yahan tak ke aap ney Jmara Aqba ko rami shuru kar di. aap ney usey saat kankariyaan maarin. har kankari key sath Allahu-Akbar kehtey they.
3082,Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey sawari par betha huwa tha. main aap ko musalsal labbaik pukartey sunta raha yahan tak ke aap ney Jamara Aqba ko rami shuru ki. jab rami shuru ki to labbaik kehna band kar diya.
3083,Hazrat Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ney khabar di ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey sawari par betha tha. aap labbaik farmatey rahey yahan tak ke aap ney Jamara Aqba ko rami shuru ki.
3084,Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey sawari par betha tha. aap labbaik pukartey rahey yahan tak ke aap ney Jamara Aqba ko rami ki.
3085,"Imam Zohri sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke hamein ye baat pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab us jamre ko rami kartey jo Mina ki qurban-gaah key qarib hai to aap usey saat kankariyaan maartey. jab bhi koi kankari maartay 'Allahu-Akbar kehtey' phir aagey badhey aur qibley ki taraf munh kar key khadey ho jatey. apney dono haath utha kar dua kartey aur badi der tak khadey rehtey, phir dusrey Jamre key paas aatey aur usey saat kankariyaan maartey. jab bhi koi kankari maartey 'Allahu-Akbar kehtey' phir baain taraf ko nichey utartey aur Baitullah ki taraf munh kar key khadey ho jatey. apney dono haath utha letey aur dua kartey, phir us Jamre key paas aatey jo ghaati key paas hai aur usey saat kankariyaan maartey, phir uskey paas (dua key liye) nahin thehertey they. Imam Zohri bayan kartey hain ke mainey ye hadees Hazrat Salim sey suni, unhoney apney baap ( Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat kartey hain. aur Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aisey hi kiya kartey they."
3086,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Mohrim (aehram ki halat mein) Jamara Aqba ko rami kar ley to uskey liye aurton key ilawa har chiz halal ho jati hai. un sey puchha gaya : khushbu? farmaya : mainey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney kastoori laga rakhi thi. kya ye khushbu nahin?
